NK038(nyi)001:1: // dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol
NK038(nyi)001:2: pa mtshon cha 'khor lo zhes bya ba'i rgyud bzhugs
NK038(nyi)001:4: sh+r+ai n+aa th+aa k+aa la a b+hi s+n+aa sa ma la l+ai ta yud+ha tsakra n+aa ma tan+t+ra /
NK038(nyi)001:6: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo zhes bya ba'i rgyud /
NK038(nyi)001:7: bcom ldan 'das dpal sgrol byed thugs rje'i rgyal po
NK038(nyi)001:8: shin tu rnam par grol ba nyid la phyag 'tshal
NK038(nyi)001:9: lo // 'di skad 'gro ba bdag gis thos pa dus gcig na /
NK038(nyi)001:10: bcom ldan 'das gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo
NK038(nyi)001:11: rje de sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams bsam gyis mi
NK038(nyi)001:12: khyab pa'i chos kyi dbyings kyi mtha' klas pa 'jig
NK038(nyi)001:13: rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med pa
NK038(nyi)001:14: na / stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten
NK038(nyi)001:15: gyi khams kyi bye brag du ma na ston pa
NK038(nyi)001:16: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas spyod yul thams
NK038(nyi)001:17: cad nas thams cad du yongs su dag pa dang
NK038(nyi)001:18: na / / rgyal po lnga ltar rdzogs longs spyod pa dang /
NK038(nyi)001:19: thub pa'i dbang po lta bu sogs pa bsam gyis
NK038(nyi)001:20: mi khyab pa'i drung na rang rang dang mthun pa'i
NK038(nyi)001:21: sku dang / mtshan gyi bye brag du ma ston cing 'khod de /
NK038(nyi)001:22: sku'i bye brag de 'dra ba re re'i 'khor na yang 'dun pa sems pa dang /
NK038(nyi)001:26: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor gyi bye brag grangs brjod kyis mi lang bas bskor nas bzhugs so //
NK038(nyi)001:27: de dang de nyid 'byung ba'i dus kun tu /
NK038(nyi)001:28: rang gi ston pa la nyan cing rang gi nyes 'khor na chos ston to //
NK038(nyi)001:30: sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal ba /
NK038(nyi)001:31: gsang sngags kyi ngo bo de nyid do //
NK038(nyi)001:32: sprul pa'i sku de dag 'das nas kyang 'byung ba'i
NK038(nyi)001:33: dus de'i 'khor gyis rtog pa sel zhing gsang sngags
NK038(nyi)001:34: ston to // de'i dus na thub pa chen po
NK038(nyi)001:35: de nyid dgongs pa gsum gyi phyir mya ngan las
NK038(nyi)001:37: de'i dus na rdzu 'phrul can bka' 'gro ba mdzad nas 'khor bsdus pas /
NK038(nyi)001:38: gang nang du yang dag par 'jog pa lnga ma
NK038(nyi)001:39: gtogs pa 'dus nas rang rang gi the tshom bcad
NK038(nyi)001:40: do // 'khor 'dus pa'i nang nas rig 'dzin rgyal
NK038(nyi)001:41: po nyid kyis gsang ba dam pa'i bstan pa rgyas
NK038(nyi)001:42: do // par nam byung / sangs rgyas nyid kyis gsang sngags mi ston nam zhus pas /
NK038(nyi)001:43: gsang sngags dus bcu gnyis kyi dus su byung /
NK038(nyi)001:45: de ltar ngas tshogs su rgyas par ma byas kyang /
NK038(nyi)001:46: dam pa'i rigs rtogs pa gsum ldan la sogs kun
NK038(nyi)001:47: la rgyas par bshad pas nga mya ngan las 'das
NK038(nyi)001:48: nas lo brgyad dang bcu gnyis kyi dus su 'byung
NK038(nyi)001:50: log pa'i bdud rnams ni kyal ka'i tshig sgrogs par 'gyur la /
NK038(nyi)001:51: de la byis pa so so'i skye bo phal che
NK038(nyi)001:52: ba myang ngan gyis gdungs shing kyi hud kyi hud
NK038(nyi)001:54: rang gi don la sems dpa' rnams ni 'da' ba med pa'i don chud de gnas so //
NK038(nyi)001:55: de nas de'i dus la bab pa'i tshe rigs can lnga ni 'di lta ste /
NK038(nyi)001:56: blo gros thabs dang ldan pa dang /
NK038(nyi)001:61: rang gi mngon par shes pas mkhyen te /
NK038(nyi)001:62: rdzu 'phrul gyis lho phyogs kyi gling tan tra'i tshal
NK038(nyi)001:63: drag shul can gyi ri la tshogs te ston pa
NK038(nyi)001:64: 'das pa dang / gsang sngags kyi theg pa ma byung ba la /
NK038(nyi)001:65: gdug pa can dang bcas te smre sngags cher bsgrags pas /
NK038(nyi)001:66: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyis gsan nas /
NK038(nyi)001:68: rin po che'i 'khor lo rtsibs dang ldan pa'i dbang
NK038(nyi)001:69: bskur nas gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa shod cig
NK038(nyi)001:70: par bka' basgo'o // de nas gsang ba'i bdag pos zhal gyis bzhes te /
NK038(nyi)001:71: thugs rje'i rdzu 'phrul gyis rang bzhin gyi skur mdzad nas /
NK038(nyi)001:72: ri ma la ya'i rtser byon no //
NK038(nyi)001:73: deng dam pa'i rig can lnga pos 'di ci yin snyam ste the tshom du gyur nas dris pa /
NK038(nyi)001:76: skyes bu chen po khyod su zhig yin /
NK038(nyi)001:78: gdung rus pha ma ci yin gang la brten /
NK038(nyi)001:81: gsang ba'i bdag pos bka' stsal ba //
NK038(nyi)001:82: nga ni cis kyang mi bskyod de //
NK038(nyi)001:83: 'gyur med rdo rje sems dpa' las //
NK038(nyi)001:84: ye shes thugs rjes 'gro don la //
NK038(nyi)001:85: byon pas gsang bdag phyag rdor yin //
NK038(nyi)001:86: srid gsum 'gro ba'i gnyen gcig yin //
NK038(nyi)001:87: stong pa chen po'i dbyings nas 'ong //
NK038(nyi)001:88: pha ni sna tshogs ma 'gags thabs //
NK038(nyi)001:89: ma ni shes rab brjod dang bral //
NK038(nyi)001:90: rdo rje rigs chen nga yi rus //
NK038(nyi)001:91: bshes gnyen phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:92: dbang bskur 'gro ba'i tshig la brten //
NK038(nyi)001:93: khyed kyi the tshom sel du 'ongs //
NK038(nyi)001:95: ye shes sgron me sbar du 'ongs //
NK038(nyi)001:96: 'khor ba'i rgya mtshor bying ba la //
NK038(nyi)001:97: thabs kyi gru gzings byed du 'ongs //
NK038(nyi)001:98: ma rig ling tog ldongs pa la //
NK038(nyi)001:100: lam stor rdzob tu 'khyams pa la //
NK038(nyi)001:102: ma rtogs don gyis dbul ba la //
NK038(nyi)001:104: rtog pa'i gzung 'dzin sgo lcags la //
NK038(nyi)001:106: ston pa mya ngan yongs mi 'da' //
NK038(nyi)001:107: chos kyang nub par mi 'gyur te //
NK038(nyi)001:108: ma rig smin mdzad 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)001:111: dam pa'i rigs can lnga pos dang ba'i sems kyis phyag btsal nas bstod do //
NK038(nyi)001:112: e ma bcom ldan gsang ba'i bdag /
NK038(nyi)001:113: bka' yi 'grel chen gsang ba'i mdo //
NK038(nyi)001:114: chos kyi me long bdud kyi dag /
NK038(nyi)001:115: sman pa'i rgyal po yid bzhin nor //
NK038(nyi)001:116: sangs rgyas kun dngos khyod phyag 'tshal //
NK038(nyi)001:118: de'i dus su mi mjed 'jig rten 'dir /
NK038(nyi)001:119: mngon sum mtshan ma'i ltas sna tshogs dang /
NK038(nyi)001:120: 'pho 'gyur dang cho 'phrul la sogs du ma yang byung ngo //
NK038(nyi)001:121: de'i dus su gsang sngags kyi rigs can lha'i tshogs dang /
NK038(nyi)001:126: dpal mgon po nag po la sogs pa ma mo'i tshogs dang /
NK038(nyi)001:127: lha ma srin sde brgyad kun 'dus te /
NK038(nyi)001:128: rang rang gi srog snying phul nas bran du khas blangs shing bstan pa bsrung bar dam bcas so //
NK038(nyi)001:129: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK038(nyi)001:130: gleng gzhi sngon gyi gtam rgyud kyi le'u ste dang po'o //
NK038(nyi)001:131: de nas 'khor de'i nang nas srin po'i rgyal po lang ka mgrin bcu zhes bya ba /
NK038(nyi)001:132: sngon gyi rgyal ba rnams la bya ba byas pa /
NK038(nyi)001:133: thub pa'i dbang po las gsang sngags kyi nges pa rnyed pa des /
NK038(nyi)001:134: ched du rang gi stan las langs nas /
NK038(nyi)001:135: e ma thugs rje'i mnga' bdag mchog /
NK038(nyi)001:136: sangs rgyas khros pa'i sku mchog dpal //
NK038(nyi)001:137: nyid kyi bka' yi las mkhan mchog /
NK038(nyi)001:138: smyon pa nag po gtum bag can //
NK038(nyi)001:139: bde mthong bar ba'i lam rnyed kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:140: sems bskyed dbang gis gzhan don du //
NK038(nyi)001:141: bzang po dus tshogs srun pa de'i //
NK038(nyi)001:142: lta spyod dkyil 'khor rnam grangs dang //
NK038(nyi)001:143: dbang dang dam tshig sgrub thabs dang //
NK038(nyi)001:144: de yi rdzas dang snying po rtogs //
NK038(nyi)001:145: las la bskul dang mtha' sdud dang //
NK038(nyi)001:146: phrin las bye brag 'bras bu dang //
NK038(nyi)001:147: rgyu rkyen gtan la dbab pa rnams /
NK038(nyi)001:149: don du bdag la bstan par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)001:151: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis zhal gyis bzhes pa'i
NK038(nyi)001:152: ting nge 'dzin las mi g.yo bar mdzad de ched
NK038(nyi)001:154: smyon pa nag po gdub rtsub can //
NK038(nyi)001:155: sangs rgyas stong gis byin brlabs pas //
NK038(nyi)001:156: btul te sgrib sbyangs thar lam bstan //
NK038(nyi)001:157: phrin las rdzogs par lung bstan nas //
NK038(nyi)001:158: rang ngam sems bskyed bya ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)001:159: bskal bzang rdzogs par bstan pa bsrungs //
NK038(nyi)001:160: de nyid lta ba spyod pa gnyis //
NK038(nyi)001:161: dkyil 'khor dag ni bdun du nges //
NK038(nyi)001:162: ji bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor dang //
NK038(nyi)001:163: phyag rgya dngos grub dkyil 'khor dang //
NK038(nyi)001:164: byang chub sems dang bsod nams tshogs //
NK038(nyi)001:165: bka' sdod pho nya drag po las //
NK038(nyi)001:166: gtad khram mnan pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK038(nyi)001:167: dbang bskur ba dang dam tshig bcu gsum dang //
NK038(nyi)001:168: mchod rten rkang dang drag thun rdzas //
NK038(nyi)001:169: bsnyen bsgrub las sbyor sngags rnams dang //
NK038(nyi)001:170: rtags dang bskul ba'i bye brag gsum //
NK038(nyi)001:171: sgrub pa'i thabs la gsum du nges //
NK038(nyi)001:172: dpa' bo gying du sgrub pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:173: rtsa ba bdun ltar sgrub pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:174: drag po gshin rje ltar sgrub pa'o //
NK038(nyi)001:175: lha ni shes pa he ru ka /
NK038(nyi)001:176: gnyen po nga 'am bye brag gsum //
NK038(nyi)001:177: sgrub pa'i thabs la gsum du nges //
NK038(nyi)001:178: dpa' bo rta mgrin dbang gis 'dul //
NK038(nyi)001:180: drag po 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed //
NK038(nyi)001:181: las rim zhi rgyas phan gdags dang //
NK038(nyi)001:182: dbang du bsdu dang dbab bsad dang //
NK038(nyi)001:183: bsreg dang gnan pa zor gyi rdzogs //
NK038(nyi)001:184: de yi rgyu dang rkyen la dbang //
NK038(nyi)001:185: btul lugs bye brag rim pa bzhin //
NK038(nyi)001:186: sngon gyi go cha gyon pa'i mthus //
NK038(nyi)001:187: rim pas bshad kyis chags pas zung //
NK038(nyi)001:189: gleng slong zhal gyis bzhes pa'i le'u ste gnyis pa'o //
NK038(nyi)001:190: de nas gnas lugs ma bcos pa'i don 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:192: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba'i //
NK038(nyi)001:193: mi bskyod zhing khams dag pa ru //
NK038(nyi)001:194: dge slong thub dka' gzhon nu yis //
NK038(nyi)001:195: khyim bdag ke'u ka ya'i bu //
NK038(nyi)001:196: dge slong thar pa nag po dang //
NK038(nyi)001:197: dan phag g.yog dang bcas pa la //
NK038(nyi)001:198: ji bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor gsungs //
NK038(nyi)001:199: ji bzhin nyid de ma bcos na //
NK038(nyi)001:200: dngos po bzhi la gnas bcas kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:201: nam mkha' la ni sprin bzhin te //
NK038(nyi)001:202: de ni rnal 'byor dam pa'i lam //
NK038(nyi)001:203: sems kyi dkyil 'khor gang gsal bas //
NK038(nyi)001:204: gsang sngags ngo bo de nyid yin //
NK038(nyi)001:205: rdo rje sems dpa'i rang bzhin te //
NK038(nyi)001:206: yon tan mtshan grangs mang du grags //
NK038(nyi)001:207: gsungs pa de yang 'di lta ste //
NK038(nyi)001:208: gnas lugs ji bzhin chos nyid de //
NK038(nyi)001:209: rnam rtog blo yis ma bcos par //
NK038(nyi)001:210: rang bzhin rnal ma'i don rtogs na //
NK038(nyi)001:211: dngos po gang la 'ang ma zhen par //
NK038(nyi)001:212: gzhi las ma g.yos gnas pa yis /
NK038(nyi)001:213: 'dod yon zhen chags la spyad kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:216: snang dang rang grol 'gyur snyam med //
NK038(nyi)001:217: de bzhin rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK038(nyi)001:218: dam pa'i lam la gnas pa yin //
NK038(nyi)001:219: sems nyid ma bcos sna tshogs 'byung //
NK038(nyi)001:220: gsal zhing rigs pa'i ngo bo'o //
NK038(nyi)001:221: dkyil zhes rang bzhin spros dang bral //
NK038(nyi)001:223: thig le rang rig ye shes de //
NK038(nyi)001:224: 'od ces bya ba snang ba'i rtsal //
NK038(nyi)001:225: rang rig ma bsgribs rang bzhin gsal //
NK038(nyi)001:226: smrar med spyod yul bral bas gsang //
NK038(nyi)001:227: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK038(nyi)001:228: yon tan 'byung gnas nyid du sngags //
NK038(nyi)001:229: mi dmigs ngang las kun 'byung bas //
NK038(nyi)001:230: ngo bo nyid ces brjod pa'o //
NK038(nyi)001:231: de la gnyen po med pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:233: mtshan pa'i bdag rtog 'joms pa'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)001:234: rdo rje zhes su bshad pa yin //
NK038(nyi)001:235: de nyid rang bzhin ma bcos pa //
NK038(nyi)001:236: gsal stong rig pa'i ye shes sems //
NK038(nyi)001:237: dngos po kun bcos dpal zhes brjod //
NK038(nyi)001:238: 'gran zla med pas bla na med //
NK038(nyi)001:239: gsal la mi g.yo byang chub sems //
NK038(nyi)001:240: phyogs ris bral zhing ma bcos pa //
NK038(nyi)001:241: chos rnams kun gyi de bzhin nyid //
NK038(nyi)001:242: ma spangs rang grol snying po nyid //
NK038(nyi)001:243: de phyir mtha' las 'das pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:244: dbu mar mi dmigs pa zhes bya //
NK038(nyi)001:245: gang ltar mos par snang bas na //
NK038(nyi)001:246: sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos gzhi yin //
NK038(nyi)001:248: sprul pa kun gyi 'byung gnas yin //
NK038(nyi)001:249: de la brten nas de 'byung bas //
NK038(nyi)001:250: kun gyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen yin //
NK038(nyi)001:251: de rtogs mun pa sel bas na //
NK038(nyi)001:252: zhing khams kun tu sgron me yi //
NK038(nyi)001:254: thugs rje thabs kyi 'byung gnas yin //
NK038(nyi)001:255: chos rnams ma 'dres rang snang bas //
NK038(nyi)001:256: kun gsal me long 'od po che //
NK038(nyi)001:257: de lta bu yi don rtogs na //
NK038(nyi)001:258: rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK038(nyi)001:259: bdag gzhan cha yis sbyod pa yang //
NK038(nyi)001:260: lta ba'i pogs su dbyung ba dang //
NK038(nyi)001:261: de las mi 'da' dam tshig bshad //
NK038(nyi)001:262: gtan nas ma rtogs sems can la //
NK038(nyi)001:263: phan pa'i spyodapa sna tshogs pas //
NK038(nyi)001:264: sgrol ba nyid dang sbyor la sogs //
NK038(nyi)001:265: mkha' la khyung dang chu la nya //
NK038(nyi)001:266: dbyer med thogs chags med par spyod //
NK038(nyi)001:267: longs spyod med bzhin thams cad spyod //
NK038(nyi)001:269: shes 'jug kun dang gzhan don du //
NK038(nyi)001:270: lam bsgoms skad cig cha bsgoms nas //
NK038(nyi)001:271: bsod nams dkyil 'khor mos slob cing //
NK038(nyi)001:272: rang bzhin rdzogs pas mchod bsnyen kun //
NK038(nyi)001:273: ji ltar spyad kyang nyid du grol //
NK038(nyi)001:274: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las //
NK038(nyi)001:275: ji bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i le'u ste gsum pa'o //
NK038(nyi)001:276: de nas phyag rgya dngos grub kyis dkyil 'khor 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:277: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK038(nyi)001:278: dbang rnams thob par ma byas par //
NK038(nyi)001:279: gsang sngags 'phrin sgrub byed pa rnams //
NK038(nyi)001:281: yi ge sgra btags ming tshogs la //
NK038(nyi)001:282: brten pa'i tshig gi rab mtshon te //
NK038(nyi)001:283: khong nas gab sbas don 'byin pa //
NK038(nyi)001:284: ston pa rdo rje'i thugs la gnas //
NK038(nyi)001:285: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yi //
NK038(nyi)001:286: 'bras bu lam du gyur pas na //
NK038(nyi)001:287: snod ldan ngang tshul bzang la bstan //
NK038(nyi)001:288: lus dang longs spyod gtong la sbyin //
NK038(nyi)001:289: gzhan du nam yang sbyin mi bya //
NK038(nyi)001:290: rmongs la 'phyar rabs gal te sbyin //
NK038(nyi)001:291: dus min par ni srog zad nas //
NK038(nyi)001:292: bsregs dang sbrebs par yun ring gnas //
NK038(nyi)001:293: nyams dga' phun sum tshogs pa yin //
NK038(nyi)001:294: gnas mchog dam pa yin 'ong bar //
NK038(nyi)001:295: tshul dang mthun pa'i rdzas rnams bsogs //
NK038(nyi)001:296: man+dala la sogs mdzes byas nas //
NK038(nyi)001:297: khrus byas lha bsgoms snying gar h+aum //
NK038(nyi)001:298: bgegs bskrad phyogs bsrung dkyil 'khor la //
NK038(nyi)001:301: sarba ta tha ga ta badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka
NK038(nyi)001:302: badz+ra kro d+hi d+ha ra ma h+aa dz+ny+aa na man+dala
NK038(nyi)001:303: h+aum / yon chab spos sogs mchod pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:304: gtor ma bdud rtsi rak+ta rnams //
NK038(nyi)001:305: rim pa bzhin du sngags kyis dbul //
NK038(nyi)001:306: thugs la 'byung la gnyis med rol //
NK038(nyi)001:308: bdag 'dra log pa'i stobs ldan gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:309: thog mtha' med pa'i dus mtha' nas //
NK038(nyi)001:311: skye ba mang po'i lus blangs pas //
NK038(nyi)001:312: sus kyang ma byas rang gi las //
NK038(nyi)001:313: de tsam cha gcig don spyad na //
NK038(nyi)001:314: de tsam don gyis sangs rgyas zin //
NK038(nyi)001:315: rang lus stong par ma phod cing //
NK038(nyi)001:316: chags pa'i mtha' la mngon zhen pas //
NK038(nyi)001:317: zug rngu'i nad kyis zin pa yis //
NK038(nyi)001:318: srid pa'i btson rar chud pa 'di //
NK038(nyi)001:319: mkha' la mdud pa brgyab pas nyes //
NK038(nyi)001:321: yas kyi rlung gis ded pas nyes //
NK038(nyi)001:322: dus gsum rgyal pa ma lus la //
NK038(nyi)001:324: rdo rje sems dpa'i yid skyobs shig /
NK038(nyi)001:325: rdo rje sems dpa' nye zhing bstan par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)001:326: bde bar gyur cig kun tu bde bar gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:327: shin tu bdag la thugs rjes khyab par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)001:328: bdag nyid shin tu bde bar gyur cig /
NK038(nyi)001:329: dngos grub thams cad bdag la myur du gsol //
NK038(nyi)001:330: phrin las thams cad dag par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)001:331: sems nyid dpal du mdzod cing thugs dges bde //
NK038(nyi)001:332: bcom ldan de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kun //
NK038(nyi)001:333: rdo rje sems kyi dkyil du bdag 'dril cig /
NK038(nyi)001:334: rdo rje 'byung po chen po'i dam tshig gis //
NK038(nyi)001:335: sems dpa' skye med klong du dag par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)001:337: kro ta kro ta ram tam sna tig kham ha la ha la yam /
NK038(nyi)001:338: dang po 'dzin pa stong pa nyid dag par bsgom mo //
NK038(nyi)001:341: badz+ra a mri ta a ho sarba ma na h+aum hri tha /
NK038(nyi)001:342: ma h+aa b+ha ling ta te dz+wo b+ha ling te h+aum /
NK038(nyi)001:343: ma h+aa rak+ta r+aa ga sh+au nya t+wa sa mu dra man+da la h+aum /
NK038(nyi)001:345: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK038(nyi)001:346: sngon du 'gro ba'i rim pa bstan pa'i le'u ste bzhi pa'o //
NK038(nyi)001:347: de nas sgrub pa'i rim pa 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:348: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK038(nyi)001:349: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK038(nyi)001:350: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK038(nyi)001:351: skyes pa nyid na'ang skyes pa med //
NK038(nyi)001:352: stong pa nyid du rab gsal ba'i //
NK038(nyi)001:353: snying rje'i yul ni bsgom bya zhing //
NK038(nyi)001:355: b+h+r+aum las dur khrod 'jigs pa'i gnas //
NK038(nyi)001:356: rang bzhin phyi nang mtha' dbus bral //
NK038(nyi)001:357: snang stong gar yang rgya ma chad //
NK038(nyi)001:358: dur khrod thod pa'i rgyu las grub //
NK038(nyi)001:360: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud dang //
NK038(nyi)001:361: gru chad bar khyams sgo gnyis brtsegs //
NK038(nyi)001:362: bskal pa me ri rab tu 'khrugs //
NK038(nyi)001:363: dregs pa khyo shug bsnol pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:364: dri za srin po gshin rje bdud //
NK038(nyi)001:365: dom dang khyu mchog ma he stag /
NK038(nyi)001:366: gzig gis barjisa te nyi dal bsam //
NK038(nyi)001:367: phyi rol zhing dang nyi ma bsal //
NK038(nyi)001:368: zhing skam gdan gyi bye brag ldan //
NK038(nyi)001:369: dbus su rgyu las rdo rje 'bar //
NK038(nyi)001:372: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bgrad //
NK038(nyi)001:373: g.yas g.yon dkar dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK038(nyi)001:374: kham nag dbu skra khro rtags brgyad //
NK038(nyi)001:375: rdo rje kha tam rnge chung g.yas //
NK038(nyi)001:376: b+han+d+ha rgyu zhags dung khrag g.yon //
NK038(nyi)001:377: dur khrod chas rdzogs gar dgu'i stabs //
NK038(nyi)001:379: thugs las h+aum bzhi gdan las spros //
NK038(nyi)001:380: sgong skyes yul du rigs ba zhi bskyed //
NK038(nyi)001:381: zhal gcig phyag gnyis khro tshul 'gying //
NK038(nyi)001:382: smug ser dmar ljang rtsa ba gnag /
NK038(nyi)001:386: ye shes me yi klong du bsgom //
NK038(nyi)001:387: rigs bzhi thugs kyi 'od zer las //
NK038(nyi)001:388: sngags brjod bardzusa skyes 'khor rnams bskyed //
NK038(nyi)001:389: nang gi rtsibs mchan gru chad la //
NK038(nyi)001:390: dkar mo rkun mo rmongs mo dang //
NK038(nyi)001:391: thal byed sbos mo g+ha sma r+ai //
NK038(nyi)001:392: sma sha tshe 'phel brgyad po bsgom //
NK038(nyi)001:393: khyams kyi phyogs mtshams rim pa ru //
NK038(nyi)001:394: seng stag wa dang khyi gdong tshogs //
NK038(nyi)001:395: bzhad dang kang ka bya rog 'ug /
NK038(nyi)001:396: mtshams su dgod de 'jigs ba'i gzugs //
NK038(nyi)001:398: ro langs ma rnams sgo bzhir bsgom //
NK038(nyi)001:399: srin mo smug nag la stsogs te //
NK038(nyi)001:400: drag mo nyer brgyad phyi khyams la'o //
NK038(nyi)001:401: bskyed la dbang bskur byin brlabs bya //
NK038(nyi)001:402: rang byung ye shes dkyil 'khor ni //
NK038(nyi)001:403: rang gi snying ga'i 'od zer las //
NK038(nyi)001:404: dbyangs dang ldan pa'i lha mo yi //
NK038(nyi)001:405: phyogs dus kun nas spyan drangs te //
NK038(nyi)001:406: phyag btsal dbang bsdu bkug bstims nas //
NK038(nyi)001:407: dang po thun mong rdzas lngas mchod //
NK038(nyi)001:408: de nas khyad par rnam gsum dbul //
NK038(nyi)001:409: sman gyis mchod rjes dngos grub blang //
NK038(nyi)001:410: gtor ma dbul zhing gsang nan sbreng //
NK038(nyi)001:411: rak+ta tshar gsum phul nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:412: ma mo rnams kyis bstod tshig dbul //
NK038(nyi)001:413: rtogs pa rgyun gyi gdul bya rnams //
NK038(nyi)001:414: ye shes ma 'dres yongs rdzogs bstod //
NK038(nyi)001:415: smon lam btab la 'dzab bsnyen dbul //
NK038(nyi)001:416: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK038(nyi)001:417: phyi nang gsang ba'i bzlas pa yis //
NK038(nyi)001:419: yab yum zhal sbyor tshul gyis ni //
NK038(nyi)001:420: 'bum mam bye ba rdzogs bar bya'o //
NK038(nyi)001:422: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las //
NK038(nyi)001:423: yi dam gyi lha phyag rgya dngos grub kyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i le'u ste lnga pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:424: de nas bsnyen pa lha'i ting nge 'dzin 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:425: gnyen po lha dang gnyis yin te //
NK038(nyi)001:426: spyi dang so sor gtang ba'o //
NK038(nyi)001:427: spyi ni nga nyid gsang ba'i bdag /
NK038(nyi)001:428: mi rtog ngang las dran rdzogs su //
NK038(nyi)001:429: mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis brjid //
NK038(nyi)001:430: rdo rje khro tshul sdig mdzub rngam //
NK038(nyi)001:431: dur khrod chas rdzogs med dpung klong //
NK038(nyi)001:432: nyid dang 'dra ba'i gnod sbyin tshogs //
NK038(nyi)001:433: du mas bskor bar gsal bsgoms nas //
NK038(nyi)001:434: snying po 'di dag rtag tu bzlas //
NK038(nyi)001:435: ni lam b+ha ra d+ha ra badz+ra p+aa ni adz+ny+aa pa ya ti h+aum /
NK038(nyi)001:436: yag sha badz+ra p+aa ni hra da ya h+aum phata /
NK038(nyi)001:437: drag po la ni gshin rje gshed //
NK038(nyi)001:438: mthing nag zhal gsum phyag drug brjid //
NK038(nyi)001:439: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dur khrod chas //
NK038(nyi)001:440: 'khor lo ral gri tho ba g.yas //
NK038(nyi)001:441: thod pa sdig mdzub phur pa g.yon //
NK038(nyi)001:442: yum dang gnyis su med par bsam //
NK038(nyi)001:443: nyi zla pad+ma gshin rje gdan //
NK038(nyi)001:444: dur khrod me yi gling na rngam //
NK038(nyi)001:445: gsang sngags 'di dag rgyun du bzlas //
NK038(nyi)001:446: a kro te ka ya man+ta ka ha na ma tha d+hany+dza h+aum phata /
NK038(nyi)001:447: dpa' bo gyi lang rta mchog dbang //
NK038(nyi)001:448: dmar smug zhal gsum phyag drug brjid //
NK038(nyi)001:449: dkar ljang zhal ldan rta mgo ljang //
NK038(nyi)001:450: pad+ma rdo rje mda' zor g.yas //
NK038(nyi)001:451: thod khrag dpal be'u gzhu 'dzin g.yon //
NK038(nyi)001:452: dur khrod rgyan ldan yum dang 'khril //
NK038(nyi)001:453: nyi dkyil chu bdag steng nas bgrad //
NK038(nyi)001:454: gsang sngags 'di dag rgyun du bzlas //
NK038(nyi)001:455: pad+m+aan+ta krita badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai ba h+aum /
NK038(nyi)001:456: ha ha hi hi hu lu hu lu h+aum phata /
NK038(nyi)001:457: bdud 'dul rdo rje srin por bsgom //
NK038(nyi)001:458: sngo nag dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad //
NK038(nyi)001:459: spyan ni 'bar ba nyi shu dgu /
NK038(nyi)001:460: kham nag ral pa srid rtser 'bar //
NK038(nyi)001:461: rdo rje'i gshog pas bar snang khengs //
NK038(nyi)001:462: ba spu lcags kyu bsregs pa 'dra //
NK038(nyi)001:463: sdom dang sdig pa dug sbrul 'phro //
NK038(nyi)001:464: 'jigs pa'i gzugs kyis sa gzhi khengs //
NK038(nyi)001:465: rdo rje thod skyog tir dbyug zhags //
NK038(nyi)001:466: nyi zla khyung dang 'ug pa khra //
NK038(nyi)001:467: rdo rje mdung rtse gsum pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:468: za ma tog dang rdul g.yab dang //
NK038(nyi)001:469: rnga chung ri rab spyi skor 'phen //
NK038(nyi)001:470: klu dbang 'bum kyis brgyan cing bklubs //
NK038(nyi)001:471: dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar ba'i dbus //
NK038(nyi)001:472: khro gnyer sdang mig rnam par rngam //
NK038(nyi)001:473: zhabs brgyad 'bar bas lha brgyad gnon //
NK038(nyi)001:474: rdo rje srin po'i khro bo'i sku //
NK038(nyi)001:475: lha dang bdud las rnam par rgyal //
NK038(nyi)001:476: gsang sngags 'di yang rtag tu bzlas //
NK038(nyi)001:477: rak+sha he ru ka r+au tra ma ta ma h+aa ha tam kro d+ha ts+wa la h+aum phata /
NK038(nyi)001:478: b+hur kum i tsi ki li uts+tshasma kro d+ha h+aum phata /
NK038(nyi)001:479: de ltar bsnyen pa'i snying po de //
NK038(nyi)001:480: chos skyong mgon po'i drag sngags yin //
NK038(nyi)001:481: rab tu gsang ba'i phrin las yin //
NK038(nyi)001:483: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK038(nyi)001:484: gnyen po stobs kyi lha bstan pa'i le'u ste drug pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:485: de nas rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:487: rang gi yid bzhin rin po che //
NK038(nyi)001:488: yod pas ma shes stor bas dran //
NK038(nyi)001:490: sngon tshe nga yi bshes gnyen mchog /
NK038(nyi)001:491: byams mgon dam pa zhig gis bstan //
NK038(nyi)001:492: e ma'o khyod kyis mi shes sam //
NK038(nyi)001:493: sgron mes mun khung gser 'tshol ltar //
NK038(nyi)001:494: gsang ba'i snying po'i mdzod brtol nas //
NK038(nyi)001:495: thig le gcig gis kun la khyab //
NK038(nyi)001:496: thams cad nges par 'dus chen ston //
NK038(nyi)001:497: 'jig rten brtan g.yo la sogs kun //
NK038(nyi)001:498: khrag 'thung lnga bcu brgyad du gnas //
NK038(nyi)001:500: btsal med ma bcos rnam par dag /
NK038(nyi)001:501: thig le yungs kar tshad tsam bsgom //
NK038(nyi)001:503: mun sel dngos po kun sbyangs nas //
NK038(nyi)001:504: thams cad ma bcos sku ru gsal //
NK038(nyi)001:505: slar 'dus thig le'i ngang du thim //
NK038(nyi)001:506: brtan nas 'od du zhu bar bsam //
NK038(nyi)001:507: ma bcos gnyug ma'i ngang du gsal //
NK038(nyi)001:508: rdzogs pa'i rlung la sbyang ba ni //
NK038(nyi)001:509: rdo rje sems dpa'i tsit+ta'i nang //
NK038(nyi)001:511: de steng bde chen sa rlung dang //
NK038(nyi)001:512: rnam par dag pa'i zla steng dang //
NK038(nyi)001:513: rdo rje rin chen rang bzhin yin //
NK038(nyi)001:514: dbus na rdo rje sems dpa' ni //
NK038(nyi)001:515: thig le 'od zer lnga dang ldan //
NK038(nyi)001:516: mgrin pa mgron po'i rlung dkyil gnyis //
NK038(nyi)001:517: sprul pa nyid ma'i me rlung gnyis //
NK038(nyi)001:518: pad+ma'i rigs dang las rigs so //
NK038(nyi)001:519: lnga ldan dbus su thig le bsam //
NK038(nyi)001:520: yang la yang du 'dres bsam nas //
NK038(nyi)001:521: rig pa sems kyi rlung zin pas /
NK038(nyi)001:523: yang na 'khor lo rnams pa lnga //
NK038(nyi)001:524: bde chen sum cu rtsa gnyis ham //
NK038(nyi)001:525: brtan pa'i thig le yi ge la //
NK038(nyi)001:526: longs spyod bcu drug lnga ldan //
NK038(nyi)001:527: chu yi sa bon yi ge bam //
NK038(nyi)001:529: brjod bral thig le yi ge mum //
NK038(nyi)001:530: sprul pa drug cu rtsa gnyis dbus //
NK038(nyi)001:531: drod du mi bzad a dang mum //
NK038(nyi)001:533: yi ge yon tan stobs kyis 'grub //
NK038(nyi)001:534: sa nyid chu la thim pa yis //
NK038(nyi)001:535: kun tu mnyam blo zag med pa'i //
NK038(nyi)001:536: lam gyi ye shes dang po skyed //
NK038(nyi)001:537: chu nyid me la thim pa yis //
NK038(nyi)001:538: zag med ro myong bde ba sdud //
NK038(nyi)001:539: me nyid rlung la thim pa yis //
NK038(nyi)001:540: 'gyur med ngang bzhin gsal ba nyid //
NK038(nyi)001:541: glog gi snang ba lta bur 'byung //
NK038(nyi)001:542: rlung nyid rnams shes nam mkha' thim //
NK038(nyi)001:543: rang gsal rig pa mar me 'dra //
NK038(nyi)001:544: phyi nang mun pa rnam par sbyangs //
NK038(nyi)001:545: nam mkha' lta bur mthong bar 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:546: phyi mas rim pas rtogs pa 'char //
NK038(nyi)001:547: bsgom pa snang bzhugs sprad la bsgom //
NK038(nyi)001:549: e ma'o dngos po med pa las //
NK038(nyi)001:550: sangs rgyas nyid dang thugs rje'i ngang //
NK038(nyi)001:551: ji ltar snang ba ma 'gags pa'o //
NK038(nyi)001:552: 'dun pa'i dus na rigs kyi bu //
NK038(nyi)001:553: yid la byed pa thob ces te //
NK038(nyi)001:554: sems gsum skye zhing mtha' kun grol //
NK038(nyi)001:555: rten pa gzhi yi rnam par gnas //
NK038(nyi)001:558: sems bzhi rtogs te mtha' bcu shes //
NK038(nyi)001:560: 'jigs pa lnga bral khyad par gsal //
NK038(nyi)001:561: yongs su mi rtog ting nge 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)001:562: rmi lam lta bur chos lung bstan //
NK038(nyi)001:563: 'jig rten nor bu rin chen gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:564: gang bar spyod pa'i ltas mthong 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:565: sgyu ma spyod pa'i skyes bu de //
NK038(nyi)001:566: 'khor los sgyur ba'i cha byad du //
NK038(nyi)001:567: rin chen bdun dang dpung tshogs kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:568: dbang sgyur thabs kyi theg pa ston //
NK038(nyi)001:569: lung chen thob pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK038(nyi)001:570: seng ge dag la zhon nas ni //
NK038(nyi)001:571: thams cad gnon pa'i rtag mthong 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:573: 'bras bu nyid la lam shes pas //
NK038(nyi)001:574: lam gyi sa ni bde rdzogs te //
NK038(nyi)001:575: gzhan dag smin par bya ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)001:576: ji ltar 'dod ltar thabs sbyor mchog /
NK038(nyi)001:577: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor bas //
NK038(nyi)001:578: kun snang ting 'dzin nyid thob pas //
NK038(nyi)001:579: snang byed nyi zla'i 'khor lo bskor //
NK038(nyi)001:580: thams cad gsal byed ltas mthong na //
NK038(nyi)001:581: gdeng du gyur pa'i ngo bo yin //
NK038(nyi)001:582: de nas rgyal tshab skyes bu des //
NK038(nyi)001:583: chos kyi rgyal po gang de yi //
NK038(nyi)001:584: gdung 'tshob dga' ldan theg chen ston //
NK038(nyi)001:585: mi gnas bcu dus cho 'phrul snang //
NK038(nyi)001:586: sa bcu don la gnas nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:587: gsang sngags don mchog ma rnyed na //
NK038(nyi)001:588: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen mi 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:589: rnyed ma thag tu de rnyed 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:590: grol bar 'dod na bla ma bsten //
NK038(nyi)001:591: rig pa rang byung ye shes nyid //
NK038(nyi)001:592: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor rdzogs //
NK038(nyi)001:594: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK038(nyi)001:595: thabs lam byang chub sems kyi le'u ste bdun pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:596: de nas bsod nams tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor 'di gsungs /
NK038(nyi)001:598: bsod nams tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ni //
NK038(nyi)001:599: zhing khams rin chen yod pa ru //
NK038(nyi)001:600: ston pa kun tu bzang po yis //
NK038(nyi)001:601: sras mchog 'jam dpal chen po la //
NK038(nyi)001:602: bshad pa bzhin du rtogs gyur na //
NK038(nyi)001:603: gang la byas kyang lam gyi grogs //
NK038(nyi)001:604: dper na me la shing snan bzhin //
NK038(nyi)001:605: mdzad spyod gsum po gdeng ldan nas //
NK038(nyi)001:606: rnal 'byor spyod lam tshul gyis rol //
NK038(nyi)001:607: de ni ji lta bu zhe na //
NK038(nyi)001:609: bza' btung gos rgyan bro gar dang //
NK038(nyi)001:610: glu tshig ga tan g+han rnam lnga'o //
NK038(nyi)001:611: skye shi med par mdzad spyod dang //
NK038(nyi)001:612: 'ching grol med par mdzad spyod dang //
NK038(nyi)001:613: mi 'byung rol pa'i mdzad spyod do //
NK038(nyi)001:614: de yi bye brag rnam gsum ste //
NK038(nyi)001:615: snang ba lha rol lha rol dang //
NK038(nyi)001:616: rang snang ye shes rol pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:617: rang bzhin nyid la rol pa'o //
NK038(nyi)001:618: de la yon tan rnam lnga ste //
NK038(nyi)001:619: bza' dang btung ba'i longs spyod kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:620: bde chen sku dang bdud rtsi 'grub //
NK038(nyi)001:621: rgyan dang bgo ba'i longs spyod kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:623: bro gar bskyod bsgul longs spyod kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:624: sra la 'dzul dang stong la rgyug /
NK038(nyi)001:625: sgra tshig sgra yi longs spyod kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:626: chos kyi dngos grub thob par 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:627: ta na g+ha na longs spyod kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:628: rang byung ye shes thob par byed //
NK038(nyi)001:629: de phyir 'byor ba'i longs spyod bya //
NK038(nyi)001:630: sems nyid rang snang 'dod yon brlabs //
NK038(nyi)001:631: bde gshegs dkyil 'khor spyan drangs la //
NK038(nyi)001:632: ting 'dzin rdzas kyis rim bzhin mchod //
NK038(nyi)001:633: bro gar glu tshig rgyan rdzogs bya //
NK038(nyi)001:634: rol mo mu stegs rol la dgug /
NK038(nyi)001:635: bsgral ba'i shes pa gnas chen spar //
NK038(nyi)001:636: yab yum mkha' la sras su bskyed //
NK038(nyi)001:637: des ni bsod nams tshogs chen ldan //
NK038(nyi)001:640: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK038(nyi)001:641: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi le'u ste brgyad pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:642: de nas bka' sdod pho nya'i dkyil 'khor 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:643: de ltar gdeng ldan sngags pa yis //
NK038(nyi)001:644: dur khrod la sogs rgya mtsho'i ma do //
NK038(nyi)001:645: ri rab ri yi rtse mo 'am //
NK038(nyi)001:646: nags tshal rtsub pa'i sa phyogs sam //
NK038(nyi)001:647: sbrul dang gcan gzan gdug pa rnams //
NK038(nyi)001:648: gnas pa de lta bu yi sa dag la /
NK038(nyi)001:650: bdud rtsi khrag gis chags chag gdab //
NK038(nyi)001:651: dur skra'i rus chen thig btab la //
NK038(nyi)001:653: lcags khang lnga dang bar khyams sgo //
NK038(nyi)001:654: lcags ri nag po khor yug phyi //
NK038(nyi)001:655: khrag dang bshang gci sha chen dang //
NK038(nyi)001:656: rkang dang klad pa klad rgyas dang //
NK038(nyi)001:657: rnag dang chu ser la sogs pa //
NK038(nyi)001:658: 'dam kyi phru ma brgyad kyis bskoor //
NK038(nyi)001:659: dbus su yab yum mchog phur dgod //
NK038(nyi)001:660: mkhar bzhi sprul pa dregs bzhi la //
NK038(nyi)001:661: lcags sam gdug shing phur pa dgod //
NK038(nyi)001:662: lho sgor thod pa mtshan ldan du //
NK038(nyi)001:663: dpal bshos khrag sna snying gi cha //
NK038(nyi)001:664: la phug la du sbyar ba yi //
NK038(nyi)001:665: byang du thod par gtor ma dang //
NK038(nyi)001:666: thod rus rkang rus klad pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:667: 'bru mar sbyar ba'i mchod pa bsham //
NK038(nyi)001:668: shar sgor 'bru yi phung po spung //
NK038(nyi)001:669: nub tu sha sna snying sna bzhag /
NK038(nyi)001:670: dbus su thod pa mtshan ldan gnyis /
NK038(nyi)001:671: steng 'og bsnyen bsgrub sngags bzhi bri //
NK038(nyi)001:672: snying gsum bdud rtsi dar bri phyi //
NK038(nyi)001:673: bar gyi sha khrag rus pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:674: rba gsang rdzas kyi ro ras kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:675: khyams la sogs pa grwa bzhir dgod //
NK038(nyi)001:676: tshil chen me mar chen po dang //
NK038(nyi)001:677: rak+ta gsang nan chang gis sbyar //
NK038(nyi)001:678: thod pa'i rnga dang rkang gi dung //
NK038(nyi)001:679: shun gyi rgyal mtshan phyogs bzhir dgram //
NK038(nyi)001:680: zhing gi bla re'i man+dala dbus /
NK038(nyi)001:681: bdag nyid khro bo ma rung bsgom //
NK038(nyi)001:683: rdo rje ra ba gur du gdams //
NK038(nyi)001:684: me ris brgyan pa'i dbus nyid du //
NK038(nyi)001:685: 'od lngar gyur pa'i gzhal yas bsam //
NK038(nyi)001:686: bla ma dkon mchog yi dam lha //
NK038(nyi)001:687: zla ba'i gdan la sngon bsam la //
NK038(nyi)001:688: sngon bzhin mchod la gsol ba gdab //
NK038(nyi)001:689: 'od zhu bdag gi sgrib pa sbyangs //
NK038(nyi)001:690: mchod gtor rgyan rnams byin gyis brlabs //
NK038(nyi)001:691: lhar gsal thugs las smug nag b+h+aum //
NK038(nyi)001:694: stong gsum shong zhing yangs par bskyed //
NK038(nyi)001:695: mi rta la sogs ro rlon gyi //
NK038(nyi)001:696: gdan steng dun las khro bo'i sku //
NK038(nyi)001:697: g+hur kung ma h+aa k+aa la kro d+ha h+aum phata //
NK038(nyi)001:698: rak+sha kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai rag+mo h+aa //
NK038(nyi)001:699: mgon po tshogs bdag chen po ni //
NK038(nyi)001:700: ljang nag zhal gsum phyag drug ste //
NK038(nyi)001:701: g.yas ser g.yon dmar ljang nag 'jigs //
NK038(nyi)001:702: kham nag dbu skra gyen du 'khyil /
NK038(nyi)001:703: spyan dgu sdang mig skar ltar 'khrug /
NK038(nyi)001:704: shun gos thod pa'i phreng ba can //
NK038(nyi)001:705: stag dang glang chen thal pa zhag /
NK038(nyi)001:706: gdug pa'i rgyan tshogs chas kyis mdzes //
NK038(nyi)001:707: g.yas kyi dang po gsal shing 'phyar //
NK038(nyi)001:708: bar ma rdo rje rtse lnga pa //
NK038(nyi)001:710: g.yon gyi dang po thod khrag 'thung //
NK038(nyi)001:711: bar pa rno dbal shun gyi mdung //
NK038(nyi)001:712: tha ma sbrul zhags srog la rngam //
NK038(nyi)001:713: zhabs bzhi gyad kyi dor thabs can //
NK038(nyi)001:714: nye gnas kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma //
NK038(nyi)001:715: 'jigs tshul zhal gcig phyag gnyis rngam //
NK038(nyi)001:716: zhing dang re sde thod sbrul brgyan //
NK038(nyi)001:717: g.yas pa rgyu zhags yab la 'khyud //
NK038(nyi)001:718: g.yon pa thod skyogs khrag gis bkang //
NK038(nyi)001:719: rus bcud rkang dang klad pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:720: 'bru mar chang gis sbyar ba yi //
NK038(nyi)001:721: rtag par rang gis longs spyod 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)001:722: 'khor bzhir khro bo gnod sbyin dang //
NK038(nyi)001:723: srin mo ma tshogs 'jigs pa bskyed //
NK038(nyi)001:724: phyi rim nye 'khor nyi shu brgyad //
NK038(nyi)001:725: srin mo nye gnas chen po brgyad //
NK038(nyi)001:726: koo ri tsoo ri phra mo ha //
NK038(nyi)001:727: be ta l+ai dang puk+ka s+ai /
NK038(nyi)001:728: g+hasma ri dang sma sha ni //
NK038(nyi)001:729: tsan+da li la sog pa kun //
NK038(nyi)001:730: rngam zhing rngam pa'i ma tshogs kun //
NK038(nyi)001:731: shin tu 'jigs pa'i gzugs su bsgom //
NK038(nyi)001:732: srin po'i bu mo dri za brgyad //
NK038(nyi)001:733: seng stag wa spyang bzhad kyi mgo /
NK038(nyi)001:734: kang ka bya rog 'ug pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)001:735: zhing la rngam zhing ston pa'i tshul //
NK038(nyi)001:736: dur khrod pa yi sgo srung bzhi //
NK038(nyi)001:737: brtson mo gdong mo gar log mo //
NK038(nyi)001:738: 'jug par byed pa'i ma mo bzhi //
NK038(nyi)001:739: gsang sgo 'dzin cing bka' sgo srungs //
NK038(nyi)001:740: dur khrod bdag mo gru 'degs bzhi //
NK038(nyi)001:741: bskam ma shin tu bskam ma dang //
NK038(nyi)001:742: ra ro ma dang khrag 'thung ma //
NK038(nyi)001:743: chags pas gdung ba'i tshul du gnas //
NK038(nyi)001:744: phyi rim slas dang byi mo bran //
NK038(nyi)001:745: ma mo bran mo gnod sbyin mo //
NK038(nyi)001:746: srin mo sha za khrag 'phrog ma //
NK038(nyi)001:747: bdud kyi ming 'dzin bla rkun mo //
NK038(nyi)001:748: blon mo dmag dpon sde dpon mo //
NK038(nyi)001:749: ru dpon pho nyar mngag par bya //
NK038(nyi)001:750: ci bgyid bka' nyan dregs pa'i 'khor //
NK038(nyi)001:751: rbod gtong rngam pa'i tshul du bsgom //
NK038(nyi)001:752: nad kyi bskal pa tshub mar gtong //
NK038(nyi)001:753: gdug pa'i mtshon cha lus la 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)001:754: mkhar dang 'ongs pas phyi rol na //
NK038(nyi)001:756: sbrang ma sbrang rgod bung ba dang //
NK038(nyi)001:757: sbrul dang sdigs pa sdom la sogs //
NK038(nyi)001:758: kang ka ru rtse 'ug pa khwa //
NK038(nyi)001:759: bya gcan sha zan tshogs 'phul zhing //
NK038(nyi)001:760: ce spyang stag seng dom dred 'phar //
NK038(nyi)001:761: dur khrod ro yi longs spyod la //
NK038(nyi)001:762: blta zhing rgyug cing ro la 'then //
NK038(nyi)001:764: de ltar gsal bar gyur pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:765: rang bzhin yul nas bkug cing bstim //
NK038(nyi)001:766: phur pas bsgral zhing zhal du gsol //
NK038(nyi)001:767: phyal du sbyangs la gnas su gdon //
NK038(nyi)001:769: rang dam bca' zhing dam tshig dbog /
NK038(nyi)001:770: mna' bor las la mngag par bsam //
NK038(nyi)001:771: brtan par byas la mchod pa bstab //
NK038(nyi)001:772: mnga' gsol phrin las gzhol ba dang //
NK038(nyi)001:773: bsnyen dang nye ba'i bsnyen pa bzlas //
NK038(nyi)001:775: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol
NK038(nyi)001:776: pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las bka' sdod pho
NK038(nyi)001:777: nya'i dkyil 'khor pa'i le'u ste dgu pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:778: de nas de dag gi dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:780: lang ka yul gyi grong rdal gyi //
NK038(nyi)001:781: dbus kyi ri bo ma la ya //
NK038(nyi)001:782: ko ka thang dmar rgya mtsho'i mdo //
NK038(nyi)001:783: byan lag mchong ri gnam lcags 'bar //
NK038(nyi)001:784: drag shul can gyi rtse mo na //
NK038(nyi)001:785: rdo rje thabs kyis blta ba'i yul //
NK038(nyi)001:786: chos 'dzin rigs kyi bsgrubs gnas su //
NK038(nyi)001:787: dpal chen rdo rje srin po yis //
NK038(nyi)001:788: bdud kyi sde rnams btul nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:789: gsang sngag 'khor lo bskor ba'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)001:790: ming gi dbang bskur bran du khas blangs pa //
NK038(nyi)001:791: rdo rje ro langs dur khrod tshogs kyi bdag /
NK038(nyi)001:792: mgon po nag po chen po dang //
NK038(nyi)001:793: nye gnas k+r+ao d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma //
NK038(nyi)001:794: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i 'khor //
NK038(nyi)001:795: lar ka'i bdag po la sogs pa'i //
NK038(nyi)001:797: sangs rgyal bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)001:799: b+hur kur ma h+aa ka la kro d+hi shwa ri
NK038(nyi)001:800: nag mo ti la ma e a ra li hring
NK038(nyi)001:801: hring dza dza / rag+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka bi
NK038(nyi)001:802: shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la phata phata
NK038(nyi)001:803: ha la ha la h+aum phata /
NK038(nyi)001:804: ta kem ta kem phata kro d+h+aa kro d+ha ram
NK038(nyi)001:805: ha ra ha ra yam tig sna tig sna ba
NK038(nyi)001:806: / badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha hasta kh+aa hi kh+aa hi h+aum h+aum sa ma ya manab+ha la /
NK038(nyi)001:809: badz+ra a mri ta ma h+aa kro d+ha am am //
NK038(nyi)001:810: am b+h+yo e a ra li dza dza /
NK038(nyi)001:811: e ma 'o dpa' bo thugs rje chung /
NK038(nyi)001:812: shin tu bde ba'i gnas dag nas //
NK038(nyi)001:813: snam du 'thon pa thugs rje chung //
NK038(nyi)001:814: de yang ci mdzad myur du mdzod //
NK038(nyi)001:815: myur du bsgral na yun du bde //
NK038(nyi)001:817: 'bangs la nan tan ma chung zhig /
NK038(nyi)001:818: slan chad bka' bzhin rjes su bgyid //
NK038(nyi)001:819: gal te bka' bzhin ma bgyis na //
NK038(nyi)001:821: bdag cag rnams kyi mgo lus snying //
NK038(nyi)001:822: rul myag tshig nas skam gyur cig /
NK038(nyi)001:823: i dan ta na ra kha na pa ra hri
NK038(nyi)001:824: tra tha ya na ma b+harti nan sa ma ya
NK038(nyi)001:825: rag sha si ti pi na badz+ra a mri ta
NK038(nyi)001:827: ma sring bu mo chung ma rnams //
NK038(nyi)001:829: pad+ma pra be sha kha tham kha tham pra be sha phata /
NK038(nyi)001:831: dbus su mchis skal ma mchis kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:833: phud la 'tshal skal ma mchis kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:834: lhag ma zhal chab bron la shog /
NK038(nyi)001:835: ye nas gdung ba'i ma sring rnams //
NK038(nyi)001:836: deng nas rgyal ba'i bka' yin gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:837: khyed kun nga yi las mkhan te //
NK038(nyi)001:838: bka' yi las byung myur du bsgrubs //
NK038(nyi)001:839: bdag kyang deng sngon las log spyad pa yis //
NK038(nyi)001:840: dpag tu med pa'i 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal rgyud //
NK038(nyi)001:841: da ni las 'phro gnyid sad pas //
NK038(nyi)001:842: bde ba can gyi zhing du myur 'gro ba'i //
NK038(nyi)001:843: rjes su bstan pa'i bka' las nyams pa de //
NK038(nyi)001:844: ji ltar ma byams bu la gdung ba bzhin //
NK038(nyi)001:845: dam tshig can la dung dung gdung bar gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:846: gang zhing sring byams ming la gdung ba bzhin //
NK038(nyi)001:847: yal dam can la lhang lhang brtse bar gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:848: mdza' mo ji srid grogs la gdung tshul bzhin //
NK038(nyi)001:849: rnal 'byor can gyis kril kril brtse bar gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:850: ji ltar g.yog rnams dpon la brtse ba ltar //
NK038(nyi)001:851: dam pa rnams la yid bzhin nor ltar khur //
NK038(nyi)001:852: brtse bar byed na ma ru bya //
NK038(nyi)001:853: gdung bar byed na sring du bya //
NK038(nyi)001:854: brtson par byed na bran du bya //
NK038(nyi)001:855: rigs rgyud 'dzin na bu mor bya //
NK038(nyi)001:857: bskul bar mgyogs na pho nyar bya //
NK038(nyi)001:858: bka' bzhin byed na bka' la gdams //
NK038(nyi)001:859: zhes sngon gyi tha tshig bstan pa'o //
NK038(nyi)001:860: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK038(nyi)001:861: spyan drangs shing sngon gyi tha tshig bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:862: de nas de dag la mchod cing mnga' gsol ba 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:864: dang po bstan pa bsrung bar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK038(nyi)001:865: bdud 'dul dbang phyug ma h+aa k+aa la'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)001:866: srin yul lang ka pu ri yi //
NK038(nyi)001:867: grong khyer gtan nas brlag mdzad cing //
NK038(nyi)001:868: lha ma srin gyi bu mo ni /
NK038(nyi)001:869: glog ma srin 'dul zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK038(nyi)001:870: lha chen mgon po nag po khyed //
NK038(nyi)001:872: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi gnas 'dir bzhugs nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:873: rnal 'byor bdag gis bcol pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK038(nyi)001:875: lcang lo can gyi ma h+aa b+han d+ha ru //
NK038(nyi)001:876: byang chub sems dang m+aam sa rak+ta dang //
NK038(nyi)001:877: dri chen ku ku chu ste rnam pa lnga //
NK038(nyi)001:878: gnyis sbyar ba yi pany+tsa a mri ta //
NK038(nyi)001:879: nag po chen po 'khor dang bcas la 'bul //
NK038(nyi)001:880: pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi //
NK038(nyi)001:883: rnal 'byor kun gyi dpal mgon mchog /
NK038(nyi)001:884: bstan pa srung bar zhal bzhes pa //
NK038(nyi)001:885: ma h+aa k+aa la mthu rtsal can //
NK038(nyi)001:886: dka' thub chen po tshur gson cig /
NK038(nyi)001:887: legs ldan nag po ma rung pa //
NK038(nyi)001:888: sha khrag dmar gyi mchod pa bzhes //
NK038(nyi)001:889: rang gi rgyal srid la gnas te //
NK038(nyi)001:890: khram la btab ba'i dgra bgegs rnams //
NK038(nyi)001:891: rol cig dgongs shig dam tshig gtso //
NK038(nyi)001:892: khyod kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:893: bse spyang khram la btab pa yi //
NK038(nyi)001:894: gshed ma bzhi la las gnyer gtod //
NK038(nyi)001:895: ma dang sring mo chung ma la //
NK038(nyi)001:896: dpa' bo khyod kyis rol bar mdzod //
NK038(nyi)001:897: dam tshig chen pos ma gtong zhig /
NK038(nyi)001:898: zhe sdang can gyi bdag po rnams //
NK038(nyi)001:899: sems can kun gyi tshe 'phrog pas //
NK038(nyi)001:900: dgra bo nyams pa'i srog dang phrol //
NK038(nyi)001:901: sha dang khrag la longs spyod kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:902: gnod sbyin chen po ma rungs pa //
NK038(nyi)001:903: bse spyang khram la btab pa yi //
NK038(nyi)001:904: gser dngul dbyig nor kun longs la //
NK038(nyi)001:905: rang gi 'dod pa'i longs spyod kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:906: sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor bdag nyid la //
NK038(nyi)001:907: yid bzhin lta bu'i dngos grub stsol //
NK038(nyi)001:908: rigs ngan sme sha can gyi tshogs //
NK038(nyi)001:909: ba glang khyi sha rta sha dang //
NK038(nyi)001:910: mi sha glang chen la sogs bzhes //
NK038(nyi)001:911: srin mo khrag 'thung ma kun la //
NK038(nyi)001:912: bsad pa'i khrag ni dron mor bcas //
NK038(nyi)001:913: bzhes shig dgra bo'i khrag la 'thung //
NK038(nyi)001:914: sprul pa'i phra men chen mo rnams //
NK038(nyi)001:915: thod rus rkang dang 'bru mar dang //
NK038(nyi)001:916: rkang dang a mri ta dang sbyar /
NK038(nyi)001:917: rdzu 'phrul grub pa'i rdzas rnams bzhes //
NK038(nyi)001:918: rigs ngan gdug pa'i ma mo rnams //
NK038(nyi)001:919: sha chen bshang gci khu ba khrag /
NK038(nyi)001:921: bdag gi nad rnams bzlog tu gsol //
NK038(nyi)001:922: dmigs pa'i dgra la rims nad thong //
NK038(nyi)001:923: srid pa'i bud med ma rung khyed //
NK038(nyi)001:924: bro gar glu tshig mchod pa bzhes //
NK038(nyi)001:925: dmigs bya 'jo tshul stabs kyis phrogs //
NK038(nyi)001:926: shor ba gzhon nu bdud mo'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)001:927: rnal 'byor chen mo'i bka' byung bas //
NK038(nyi)001:928: sngags sgra drag po'i mchod pa bzhes //
NK038(nyi)001:929: dgra bo'i phung po rdul du rlog /
NK038(nyi)001:930: log 'dren can gyi tshogs kun nyon //
NK038(nyi)001:931: yang dag nyid du kun rig na //
NK038(nyi)001:932: me chu las gnyis gang byas na //
NK038(nyi)001:933: gnyis kyi dbang du mi 'gyur zhing //
NK038(nyi)001:935: gsang tshig ston pa'i tshogs rnams nyon //
NK038(nyi)001:936: bshang gci khrag dang sol khu yis //
NK038(nyi)001:937: brgya 'am stong du gso nas ni //
NK038(nyi)001:938: li d+ga bcad nas sangs rgyas 'jig /
NK038(nyi)001:939: dam rdzas mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK038(nyi)001:940: bcol ba'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)001:941: mnga' bdag chen po ma rungs pa //
NK038(nyi)001:942: rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa ste //
NK038(nyi)001:943: khro bo'i rgyal po gying chen po //
NK038(nyi)001:944: mnga' bdag bdud kyi rgyal po zhes //
NK038(nyi)001:946: sngon gyi bskal ba bzang po la //
NK038(nyi)001:947: khas blangs dam bcas mna' bor ba'i //
NK038(nyi)001:948: sngon du rigs 'dzin gong mas bsgrubs //
NK038(nyi)001:949: da lta rnal 'byor dam la spyon //
NK038(nyi)001:950: bam ri thod pa mkhar gyi rtser //
NK038(nyi)001:951: ru mtshon nag po pu ru ru //
NK038(nyi)001:952: mtshon cha mang po char du 'bebs //
NK038(nyi)001:953: bdud bya nag po lding zhing 'jum //
NK038(nyi)001:954: dur khrod rgyan cha mang po rnams //
NK038(nyi)001:955: mche gtsigs rngam pa'i zhal gdangs nas //
NK038(nyi)001:956: khro bo khro mo sprul ba 'khrigs //
NK038(nyi)001:957: srin po srin mo rkan sgra rdebs //
NK038(nyi)001:958: gnod sbyin pho mo 'brug sgra sgrogs //
NK038(nyi)001:959: za byed pho mo glog ltar 'khyug /
NK038(nyi)001:960: so so'i mos pa tha dad pa'i //
NK038(nyi)001:961: dam rdzas mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK038(nyi)001:962: ji ltar bcol pa'i phrin las mdzod //
NK038(nyi)001:963: m+aam sa rak+ta go ro tsa na ba su ta g+ha na tsit+ta kh+aa ram kh+aa hi //
NK038(nyi)001:964: phrin las gzhol pa gang 'dod sbyar //
NK038(nyi)001:965: bsnyen dus smon lam 'di ltar gdab //
NK038(nyi)001:967: mgon po khyed mchod byin rlabs kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:968: phyogs dang dus ni thams cad du //
NK038(nyi)001:969: sems can legs don 'byor pa la /
NK038(nyi)001:970: dgra bgegs rnam pa kun med shog /
NK038(nyi)001:971: rta dang ba glang nor dang 'bru //
NK038(nyi)001:972: bu tsha pha ma gnyen bshes rnams //
NK038(nyi)001:973: dge zhing tshe ring nad med par //
NK038(nyi)001:974: thams cad 'byor ba ldan par shog /
NK038(nyi)001:975: 'gro ba nyes med bde gyur cig /
NK038(nyi)001:976: nad dang mu ge kun bral nas //
NK038(nyi)001:977: rgyal po dge zhing des pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:978: chos kyi rgyal srid skyong bar shog /
NK038(nyi)001:979: bde bar gshegs pa'i bstan pa ni //
NK038(nyi)001:980: phyogs bcu kun tu rgyas pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:981: myur du sems can thams cad kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:982: chos kyi snod du 'gyur bar shog /
NK038(nyi)001:983: dge ba chos bcas spyan bsngo zhing //
NK038(nyi)001:984: mgon po khyod mchod byin rlabs kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:985: bdag bcag 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK038(nyi)001:986: longs spyod rnam gnyis rdzogs par smon //
NK038(nyi)001:987: bdag cag byang chub mchog thob nas //
NK038(nyi)001:990: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las //
NK038(nyi)001:991: bsnyen pa'i las gzhung bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu gcig pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:992: de nas yang dag bshad bya ba //
NK038(nyi)001:993: gsang sngags bstan pa 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:994: b+hur kur ma h+aa pad+ma rde b+hur tsi b+hur byig gi bye ma nas se /
NK038(nyi)001:995: e ho sho mos kro d+ha h+aum h+aum phata phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK038(nyi)001:996: b+hu ru ku ru rma a pra rna /
NK038(nyi)001:997: bud tsi gi phyi ma se kha sho mo kro d+ha h+aum h+aum phata phata /
NK038(nyi)001:998: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen no //
NK038(nyi)001:999: b+hu ru ku ru i phyi uts+tsha kro d+ha h+aum phata /
NK038(nyi)001:1001: sarba sid+d+hi pha la h+aum a /
NK038(nyi)001:1002: o badz+ra tsit+ta sa ma ya a mri ta h+aum phata /
NK038(nyi)001:1003: h+r+aih badz+ra rag ta gri h+na gri h+na ra ga ma h+aa k+aa ru ni h+aum phata /
NK038(nyi)001:1004: badz+ra kro d+ha r+aa dza ya ha na ha na
NK038(nyi)001:1005: da ha da ha pa tsa pa tsa gri sna
NK038(nyi)001:1007: sgrub dang sgrub chen blang ba dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1008: mthing nag dar chen nang du ni //
NK038(nyi)001:1009: yungs kar rgyal po khrag sna dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1010: tsan+dana dmar po sbyar ba dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1011: tsan tan dkar po bzang drug dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1012: bdud rtsi skyang ba'i thum po gsum //
NK038(nyi)001:1013: dang po bar dang tha ma gtums /
NK038(nyi)001:1014: h+r+aihls bdud rtsi sbyar ba dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1015: r+aa las chags pa'i rang bzhin dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1016: h+aum las khro bor brlab pa'i sngags //
NK038(nyi)001:1017: badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la sa ma ya h+aum //
NK038(nyi)001:1018: yak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya //
NK038(nyi)001:1019: rak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya //
NK038(nyi)001:1020: tsa tra dz+wa la sa ma ya /
NK038(nyi)001:1022: phyogs bzhir sprul pa bskyed pa'o //
NK038(nyi)001:1023: de kas dgug dang bsad pa 'grub //
NK038(nyi)001:1024: b+hur kur ma h+aa ka la n+ri thum lam thum
NK038(nyi)001:1025: ri la rbad bu ni dzi dgra bo'i snying la
NK038(nyi)001:1026: ya / trag rak+sha thum ril rbad /
NK038(nyi)001:1027: dgra bo'i snying kha rag ni dza b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)001:1028: rbad pa'i gsang sngags mchog yin no //
NK038(nyi)001:1029: dmigs pa'i rnam shes dgug pa yin //
NK038(nyi)001:1030: ma h+aa k+aa la ni dza snying la thum ril ru pa ya /
NK038(nyi)001:1031: rbad su rbad su n+ri shag tsit+ta ya rbad //
NK038(nyi)001:1034: srog la srog rtsa la brems brems ya y+aa //
NK038(nyi)001:1035: hab hab n+ri ma ra ya rbad phata /
NK038(nyi)001:1036: rnam shes bsad pa'i dkyil 'khor yin //
NK038(nyi)001:1037: drag po'i phur pa skabs su gdab //
NK038(nyi)001:1038: ma h+aa k+aa li ma b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)001:1039: ru lu ru lu sa ma ya b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)001:1040: trag rak+sha la mun tra b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)001:1041: ru lu m+aa r+aa ya thun b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)001:1042: trag mo drag snying khrag m+aa ra ya thun y+aa /
NK038(nyi)001:1043: trag mo trag mo thun ya /
NK038(nyi)001:1044: sh+ri ge g+ho dza shag rbad /
NK038(nyi)001:1045: mu ro tsit+ta ni shag rbad /
NK038(nyi)001:1046: re ge sho na ni shag rbad /
NK038(nyi)001:1047: ya me to sha ni shag rbad /
NK038(nyi)001:1048: tsit+ta re ma ni shag rbad /
NK038(nyi)001:1049: sho ra du na khram badz+ra ma ti srog la rbad rbad /
NK038(nyi)001:1050: ma tshogs thun dang drag pos bsad //
NK038(nyi)001:1051: bar du dril byin bya ba yin //
NK038(nyi)001:1052: ri li ri li snying li li ri shig phru lu lu /
NK038(nyi)001:1054: tsit+ta'i dkyil du n+ri dza thun //
NK038(nyi)001:1055: khrag gi ser chen phob phob //
NK038(nyi)001:1056: ces pa zor sngags drag po yin //
NK038(nyi)001:1058: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK038(nyi)001:1059: gsang sngags bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:1060: de nas bsnyen bsgrub kyi rim pa 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:1061: bdag nyid lha yi nga rgyal gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:1062: dkyil 'khor dbus kyi phur pa la //
NK038(nyi)001:1063: dkar nag dmar ba'i gzungs thag sgril //
NK038(nyi)001:1064: mthing nag dar gyi phur pa gsum //
NK038(nyi)001:1065: bskul dang chags dang gzhil ba'i rdzas //
NK038(nyi)001:1066: pha wang dag la hri hri dza dag zi //
NK038(nyi)001:1067: h+aum dang bcas pa'i yungs kar la //
NK038(nyi)001:1068: khrag la mchod sgong hri dang mo //
NK038(nyi)001:1069: de bzhin lcags thig yi ge bdun /
NK038(nyi)001:1070: yum dang sbrel ba'i bla rdo yin //
NK038(nyi)001:1071: sman la yi dam snying po 'am //
NK038(nyi)001:1072: dpa' bo 'bru lnga bris la gzhug /
NK038(nyi)001:1073: gzungs thag sbrel la 'chang par bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1074: thugs kar rdo rje srin po 'jigs //
NK038(nyi)001:1075: mtshon cha 'khor lo bskor bar bsam //
NK038(nyi)001:1076: sngags kyi 'od zer rno la myur //
NK038(nyi)001:1077: lcags kyu'i tshul du spros nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:1078: rang bzhin mgon po'i snying ga nas //
NK038(nyi)001:1080: dus las rang gi snying pos bskor //
NK038(nyi)001:1081: de nas bzung nas mi gtong bar //
NK038(nyi)001:1082: gnas nas bkug la rten la bstims //
NK038(nyi)001:1083: bdag gi bka' nyan gsung sdod pa //
NK038(nyi)001:1084: zhi ba'i zhal dang ldan par bsam //
NK038(nyi)001:1085: 'bum phrag gcig tu rdzogs par bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1086: de nas nye ba gnas kyis bsnyen //
NK038(nyi)001:1087: thun gyi sngags kyi 'od zer nyid //
NK038(nyi)001:1088: rdo rje srin po'i mtshon char spro //
NK038(nyi)001:1089: mgon po dbang med bkug nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:1090: rang snying srog nas drod langs shing //
NK038(nyi)001:1091: lus ngag yid gsum tsha zhing bsreg /
NK038(nyi)001:1092: dbang med drung 'dug las rnams gyad //
NK038(nyi)001:1093: 'bum phrag gcig tu rdzogs par bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1094: de nas nye ba'i rtags ni 'byung //
NK038(nyi)001:1095: sman gyi thum po bdud rtsi yis //
NK038(nyi)001:1096: sku yi tsha ba gzhil phyir gtor //
NK038(nyi)001:1097: sku gsum rang bzhin rnal ma ni //
NK038(nyi)001:1098: bdag la nye zhing las rnams byed //
NK038(nyi)001:1099: tshogs dang bdud rtsi gtor mas mchod //
NK038(nyi)001:1100: dngos grub bdag blang bya ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)001:1101: bsgrub pa'i rim pa bag tsam sbyar //
NK038(nyi)001:1102: rak+ta de ni rten la gtor /
NK038(nyi)001:1103: thugs rjes chags pa bskyed par bsam //
NK038(nyi)001:1104: 'od zer lcags kyu dbang gi mchog /
NK038(nyi)001:1105: 'phros te rang bzhin mgon po la //
NK038(nyi)001:1106: dam tshig bskul zhing mchod par bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1107: sid+d+hi rtags pa'i mdog lta bu //
NK038(nyi)001:1108: bsdus shing rang la bstim par bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1109: phyed shas tsam gyis gnad la phebs /
NK038(nyi)001:1110: rten gyi thod pa kha phye la //
NK038(nyi)001:1111: myos pa'i rdzas dang bu ram dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1112: bdud rtsi 'o bskol zhal zas dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1113: de bzhin mchod pa kun kyang btang //
NK038(nyi)001:1114: dmar ljang dar gyi lid+ga bri //
NK038(nyi)001:1115: rdzas nyid bdud rtsir brlabs nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:1116: nang du srog gsum yi ge bsgom //
NK038(nyi)001:1117: mgon po'i gzhung bsrang snying po bzlas //
NK038(nyi)001:1118: drug gi sngags kyi 'od zer 'phro zhing //
NK038(nyi)001:1119: brgyad kyis sid+d+hi'i mthu byin bsdu //
NK038(nyi)001:1120: 'bum phrag rdzogs nas srod gsum ba zhu //
NK038(nyi)001:1121: sid+d+hi rdzas la bdag nyid rol //
NK038(nyi)001:1122: dam can gtor ma tshogs kyis mchod //
NK038(nyi)001:1123: sman gyi mchod pas stobs ldan 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:1124: bsnyen pa'i rdul tshon zhal phye la //
NK038(nyi)001:1125: drag po'i las la sbyar bar bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1126: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las //
NK038(nyi)001:1127: bsnyen bsgrub gnad kyi le'u ste bcu gsum pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:1128: de nas 'brub khung drag po'i dkyil 'khor 'di gsung so //
NK038(nyi)001:1130: rak+ta khrag gi dmar po byug /
NK038(nyi)001:1131: dbus nas mnyam pa'i shing gzhag la //
NK038(nyi)001:1132: man+dala zlum po bskor nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:1133: mtho gang tshad du gyen du brtsig /
NK038(nyi)001:1134: dbus nas khru gang gru gsum la //
NK038(nyi)001:1135: nang rim gsum ldan thur du bru //
NK038(nyi)001:1136: tha ma thod pa'i phreng bas brgyan //
NK038(nyi)001:1137: dug shing rtsang dmar nyi shu brgyad //
NK038(nyi)001:1138: rdo rje 'khor lo ral gri dbyug tho rgya gram lngas //
NK038(nyi)001:1139: 'og ma dag la bskor bar bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1140: dmigs pa dgra yi rdzas rnams dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1141: bag phye sa spyin bsres pa'i gzugs //
NK038(nyi)001:1142: bcu gnyis sor tshad mi rus mngag /
NK038(nyi)001:1144: dred mo'i skra thag sngo dmar gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:1145: bcings la gzugs brnyan rtsang la gdags //
NK038(nyi)001:1146: bcings la mgo brnyan dag kyang gdags //
NK038(nyi)001:1147: dur khrod g.yam pa khru gang la //
NK038(nyi)001:1148: dbus nas mtho gang gru gsum khru //
NK038(nyi)001:1149: 'brub steng bzhag la thod mkhar brtsegs //
NK038(nyi)001:1150: rgya ni de dang mthun pa la //
NK038(nyi)001:1151: dpangs su khru gang sor bzhi btod //
NK038(nyi)001:1152: rang ngos thel la sgo bstan la //
NK038(nyi)001:1153: logs bzhi 'phrin las glo dkar bzhi //
NK038(nyi)001:1154: phyogs bzhi mkhar bzhir phyed phyed bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1155: dur khrod tshon gyi ri mo yis //
NK038(nyi)001:1156: stag dang mi rta bya rgod mgo /
NK038(nyi)001:1157: srin po'i thod pa ba gam bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1158: nang du rten gyi phur pa lnga //
NK038(nyi)001:1159: yang na bka' rten brag nag dreg /
NK038(nyi)001:1160: dur khrod sa la srin po'i gzugs byas la //
NK038(nyi)001:1161: tshon gyis bsgyur la phyag mtshan gtad //
NK038(nyi)001:1162: gru bzhir ru mtshon nag po bzhi //
NK038(nyi)001:1163: phyogs bzhir bdud bya nag po lding //
NK038(nyi)001:1164: smyug ma tshigs lnga'i mda' gcig la //
NK038(nyi)001:1165: dri med drag po btsug nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:1166: bya rgod srin bya khra 'ug khwa //
NK038(nyi)001:1167: lnga sgron mda' la dar nag gdags //
NK038(nyi)001:1168: g.yu mig nam mkha' nag po la //
NK038(nyi)001:1169: rgod kyi sgro gsum dar gyis brgyan //
NK038(nyi)001:1170: dbus kyi mkhar steng gzhag par bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1171: g.yas g.yon yab yum gtor ma gzhag /
NK038(nyi)001:1172: snying gsum dar sgril lus la bcang //
NK038(nyi)001:1173: gying gi mkhar gyi steng logs gsum //
NK038(nyi)001:1174: lcags phur bcu gnyis dar gyis brgyan //
NK038(nyi)001:1175: ral gri mtho gang gri khrag byug /
NK038(nyi)001:1176: pho snying sna tshogs gtor ma bca' //
NK038(nyi)001:1177: lho phyogs gnod sbyin mkhar stengs su //
NK038(nyi)001:1178: bse mdung smug po dar gyis brgyan //
NK038(nyi)001:1179: zor mda' mon thod g.yas g.yon dgod //
NK038(nyi)001:1180: ru skyogs nang du dam rdzas bsog /
NK038(nyi)001:1181: rta dmar bya dmar gri bo'i don //
NK038(nyi)001:1182: mar khu sbrang rtsi 'o ma khrag /
NK038(nyi)001:1183: sbyar ba'i bdud rtsi'i gtor ma bsham //
NK038(nyi)001:1184: nub phyogs srin po'i mkhar stengs su //
NK038(nyi)001:1185: sbrul sha dug dang bag phye sbyar //
NK038(nyi)001:1186: sbrul mgo gsum ldan 'khyil ba bca' //
NK038(nyi)001:1187: kan+d+ha'i dgra gzugs steng du bzhag /
NK038(nyi)001:1188: g.yas su sha rul khrag rul dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1189: snying sna tshogs dang thod pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1190: g.yon du ba dmar 'o ma la //
NK038(nyi)001:1191: klu sman btab la mkhar gzhong bzhag /
NK038(nyi)001:1192: byang du za byed mkhar stengs su //
NK038(nyi)001:1193: tshon drug nam mkha' dar nag brgyan //
NK038(nyi)001:1194: gtor ma tshil chen sprin khebs can //
NK038(nyi)001:1195: lid+ga rma bya'i gdugs dang bcas //
NK038(nyi)001:1196: mkhar rnams kun gyi rgyu dag ni /
NK038(nyi)001:1197: bka' rten chos khri dur khrod dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1198: gnod sbyin sbrul dang rgyal po'i mkhar //
NK038(nyi)001:1199: phyug po'i bang mdzod ri mtho'i rtse //
NK038(nyi)001:1200: sa sna bdun la klu chus sbru //
NK038(nyi)001:1201: byan klag mchongs kyi ri bo la //
NK038(nyi)001:1202: dug shing yal ga dur khrod kyi //
NK038(nyi)001:1203: sha rus la sogs bcad phor dgram //
NK038(nyi)001:1204: kang ka thang dang mtsho 'gram la //
NK038(nyi)001:1205: dpal gtor bdud rtsi rak+ta dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1206: spos chen snum chen la sogs dgram //
NK038(nyi)001:1207: gru bzhi ha ha'i rgyal mtshan te //
NK038(nyi)001:1208: zhing gi bla re man+dala dbub //
NK038(nyi)001:1209: mon thod nang du dug sna dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1210: khrag sna phye gsum mtshon dbal brdar //
NK038(nyi)001:1211: chang gis sbyar la byang du dgod //
NK038(nyi)001:1212: de bzhin rigs ngan thod pa ru //
NK038(nyi)001:1213: yungs dkar yungs nag ske tshe dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1214: tsha ba sna tshogs lho ru dgod //
NK038(nyi)001:1215: de ltar bca' gzhi rdzogs pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1216: phyogs bcing gsol ba sngar bzhin gdab //
NK038(nyi)001:1217: dpal gyi las gzhung rdzogs par bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1218: de brgyad 'bru brgyad rbad bsad bsgyur //
NK038(nyi)001:1220: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK038(nyi)001:1221: drag po 'brub gzhung bca' gzhi'i ste bcu bzhi pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:1222: de nas yang rim pa 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:1223: bdag nyid lha yi nga rgyal la //
NK038(nyi)001:1224: thugs kar rim pa lnga rim du //
NK038(nyi)001:1225: bam las byan glag khrom las ri //
NK038(nyi)001:1226: sta na b+ha ti dur khrod gnas //
NK038(nyi)001:1227: h+aum las thod pa'i mkhar lnga bskyed //
NK038(nyi)001:1228: dbus su dmigs pa'i dgra stengs su //
NK038(nyi)001:1229: dun las rtsa ba'i sngags brjod pas //
NK038(nyi)001:1230: legs ldan yab yum sngon bzhin bskyed //
NK038(nyi)001:1231: yang na zhal gcig phyag gnyis ljang //
NK038(nyi)001:1232: gsal shing phyar zhing shun gyi mdung //
NK038(nyi)001:1233: dur khrod chas rnams rdzogs par bsam //
NK038(nyi)001:1234: mdun na las kyi bka' sdod ni //
NK038(nyi)001:1235: drag po gri gug thod pa 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)001:1236: phyogs bzhir gtso bo'i 'od spros la //
NK038(nyi)001:1237: sngags bskyed 'khor dang bcas pa bskyed //
NK038(nyi)001:1238: shar du khro chen ging ka ra //
NK038(nyi)001:1239: mthing nag mtshon cha'i 'khor lo bskor //
NK038(nyi)001:1240: snying khrag 'thung zhing dmigs pa gnon //
NK038(nyi)001:1241: phyi nang gri thogs bcu gnyis gying //
NK038(nyi)001:1242: rdo rje myu gu chos dang las //
NK038(nyi)001:1243: rin chen myu gu 'khor lo rtsal //
NK038(nyi)001:1244: zla ba'i rtsal dang nyi ma'i mdangs //
NK038(nyi)001:1245: yi ge nam mkha' spyang ki dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1246: dus mtshams phyogs 'dul dur khrod bdag /
NK038(nyi)001:1247: kun kyang rab tu 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK038(nyi)001:1248: dur khrod rgyan ldan gar thabs rgyug /
NK038(nyi)001:1249: zangs gri phyar zhing glo snying za //
NK038(nyi)001:1251: lho ru ya mas gshin rje'i gtso //
NK038(nyi)001:1252: dmar nag zhing gyon ral pa khrag /
NK038(nyi)001:1253: gser gyi ral gri mdung dmar 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)001:1254: yum ni byad thag nad rkyal rdeb //
NK038(nyi)001:1255: skyes bu bzhi dang bse mo bzhi //
NK038(nyi)001:1256: mi dmar shan pa bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK038(nyi)001:1257: 'jig rten skyong ba'i cha lugs rdzogs //
NK038(nyi)001:1258: nub tu dza las r+aa hu la //
NK038(nyi)001:1259: dud ka mgo dgu ro smad sbrul //
NK038(nyi)001:1260: mgo lus kun gsal ral pa khrag /
NK038(nyi)001:1261: gri gug thod pa bsnams pa yi //
NK038(nyi)001:1262: srin po bcu dang srin mo bcu //
NK038(nyi)001:1263: mtshon cha rno dbal longs spyod 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)001:1264: byang du ma las za byed ma //
NK038(nyi)001:1265: mthing nag khrag ral dug rlangs can //
NK038(nyi)001:1266: shun gos re lde rgyu phreng zhags //
NK038(nyi)001:1267: bse sbrul nyi zla chas kun rdzogs //
NK038(nyi)001:1268: g.yas pa khram shing nad rkyal g.yon //
NK038(nyi)001:1269: dre'u nag zhon nas me rlung 'tshubs //
NK038(nyi)001:1271: gzhan yang ma tshogs 'bum gyis bskor //
NK038(nyi)001:1273: rang bzhin gnas nas spyan drangs la //
NK038(nyi)001:1274: dur khrod gnas su rten la bstim //
NK038(nyi)001:1275: dam tshig sbyin pa 'di la brjod //
NK038(nyi)001:1276: sngon tshe dpal chen khro bo'i rgyal //
NK038(nyi)001:1277: bdud 'dul rdo rje srin po yis /
NK038(nyi)001:1278: dregs pa bcom nas sgrib pa sbyangs //
NK038(nyi)001:1279: dbang bskur ming btags srog yig phul //
NK038(nyi)001:1280: pho brang kun la dam tshig sbyin //
NK038(nyi)001:1281: phyi yi mtshan nas bos pa'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)001:1282: mgon po legs ldan nag po bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1283: nang gi mtshan nas bos ba'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)001:1284: bdud 'dul dur khrod sgrol ba'i ging //
NK038(nyi)001:1285: gsang ba'i mtshan nas bos pa'i tshe //
NK038(nyi)001:1286: rdo rje sgrol byed drag po rtsal //
NK038(nyi)001:1287: mna' bor khas blangs ma bsnyel bar //
NK038(nyi)001:1288: sku gsungs thugs su bdag sbyor ba //
NK038(nyi)001:1290: rtag tu dam tshig tshul bzhin gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:1293: de nas mchod pa tshul bzhin dbul //
NK038(nyi)001:1294: de nas rten la gzungs thag gdags //
NK038(nyi)001:1295: sgrub sngags drag po bcu bzhi pa //
NK038(nyi)001:1296: dbang med srog yig tshab ba skyed //
NK038(nyi)001:1297: myur du bkug la rten la bstim //
NK038(nyi)001:1298: skabs su sman gyi tsha ba gazha la //
NK038(nyi)001:1299: gtor ma sha khrag mchod pa brtag /
NK038(nyi)001:1300: dgongs ka rten la yungs kar brab //
NK038(nyi)001:1301: gdug sems cher bskyed dgra la bskul //
NK038(nyi)001:1302: bcu bzhi'i mtha' la rbad sngags gdags //
NK038(nyi)001:1303: skabs su sprul ba'i sngags bzhi po //
NK038(nyi)001:1304: 'bar ba'i dam tshig dmigs pa yi //
NK038(nyi)001:1305: srog la b+h+yo b+h+yo sbyar la brab //
NK038(nyi)001:1306: yungs kar khro bo'i dbal gyis brab //
NK038(nyi)001:1307: sde bzhi sprul pa 'khor bcas kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:1308: dmigs pa'i dgra yi yul khams bkang //
NK038(nyi)001:1309: bla dang shes pa bkug cing bstim //
NK038(nyi)001:1310: lha tshogs bskul dang pho nya rbad //
NK038(nyi)001:1312: phur ma khrag sbyangs sku la gtor //
NK038(nyi)001:1313: thugs rje chen pos chags pa skyes //
NK038(nyi)001:1314: dmigs pa'i 'brub khung khram la gdab //
NK038(nyi)001:1315: kun kyang byi ru'i mdog ltar gsal //
NK038(nyi)001:1317: thugs rje stobs kyis dgra 'joms sku lnga'o //
NK038(nyi)001:1318: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku yi lam mkhan po //
NK038(nyi)001:1319: dpal mgon ljang sngon drag po gsal shing can //
NK038(nyi)001:1320: khyod kyis bstan pa bshig pa bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)001:1321: gnas 'dir 'dug la bka' yi dam tshig srungs //
NK038(nyi)001:1322: sgrub pa'i grogs gyis dgra la rtags rnams phyung //
NK038(nyi)001:1324: drag po sku lnga rgyal ba'i bka' sdod mchog /
NK038(nyi)001:1325: ye shes lnga ldan rgyal ba rigs lnga'i 'khor //
NK038(nyi)001:1326: phrin las bdud 'dul dgra bgegs kun gyi gshed //
NK038(nyi)001:1327: gnas 'dir tshur spyon bdag gi phrin las mdzod //
NK038(nyi)001:1329: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las //
NK038(nyi)001:1330: drag po phrin las sgrub pa'i le'u ste bco lnga pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:1331: sgrub pa nyams su lon pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1332: drag po bsad las bya ba ste //
NK038(nyi)001:1333: dang po yungs kar dpal gyi bskul //
NK038(nyi)001:1334: tha ma bdud rtsi'i tshab gzhi la //
NK038(nyi)001:1335: rak+tasa las zhen drag po kun //
NK038(nyi)001:1336: sgrub pa'i skabs las 'dir shes bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1337: nyin mo thun ston rbad cing dgug /
NK038(nyi)001:1338: thun smad bsad pa'i drag sngags sbrel //
NK038(nyi)001:1339: lha dang dbral phyir sme rdzas gdab //
NK038(nyi)001:1340: dgongs ka pho yi reg chod kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:1341: skam thun thun khung nang du bstim //
NK038(nyi)001:1342: mchog phur nang nas gdab par bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1343: dregs pa pho rnams srog la rub //
NK038(nyi)001:1344: bka' sdod las kyi shan pa yis //
NK038(nyi)001:1345: gri gug khog gshags snying phyung nas //
NK038(nyi)001:1346: gtso bo'i zhal du stob par bsam //
NK038(nyi)001:1347: gnod sbyin tshogs dang mche gshog gis //
NK038(nyi)001:1348: sha khrag za zhing rgyu ma 'dren //
NK038(nyi)001:1349: pho gshed gnad kyi reg chod kyis /
NK038(nyi)001:1350: dgra bo bsgral ba'i phrin las so //
NK038(nyi)001:1351: mtshan mo sgrub sngags gnyis po la //
NK038(nyi)001:1352: bsad sngag spel la drag tu bzlas //
NK038(nyi)001:1353: tho rengs mo yi reg chod kyis /
NK038(nyi)001:1354: dug khrag gshed thun drag tu brdeg /
NK038(nyi)001:1355: ma mo srin mo gnod sbyin mo //
NK038(nyi)001:1356: bdud mo'i tshogs kyi dmag tshogs kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:1357: dmigs pa'i lus la nad mtshon char //
NK038(nyi)001:1359: sngo dmar dug gis rtsa rnams khengs /
NK038(nyi)001:1360: snying la 'dus nas dwangs snyigs phye //
NK038(nyi)001:1361: dwangs ma chos nyid bde bar thim //
NK038(nyi)001:1362: phung po sha khrag ma tshogs rol //
NK038(nyi)001:1363: zhag grangs dgu yi ting 'dzin bstar //
NK038(nyi)001:1364: thun rdzogs dngos dang 'brel ba'i gzungs //
NK038(nyi)001:1365: byang shar lcags mkhar sgo med du //
NK038(nyi)001:1366: dug shing me btab thun brab brdeg /
NK038(nyi)001:1367: gser phud lha srin mchod byas la //
NK038(nyi)001:1368: zor gyi lam phye bse mda' la /
NK038(nyi)001:1369: thun khrag byug la me la bsreg /
NK038(nyi)001:1370: mu stegs log lta'i thod pa ru //
NK038(nyi)001:1371: thun khrag blugs la ngad rlangs bstim //
NK038(nyi)001:1373: sngags kun dril mthar zor sngags gdags //
NK038(nyi)001:1374: de nas bskul ba 'di yang bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1375: h+aum phyogs bzhi dregs pa'i yul mkhar nas /
NK038(nyi)001:1376: zor gyi bdag po mched bzhi bzhengs //
NK038(nyi)001:1377: shar phyogs gnod sbyin stag thabs dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1378: lho phyogs drag po gshin rje'i rdo //
NK038(nyi)001:1379: nub phyogs bdud nag mgo dgu pa //
NK038(nyi)001:1380: byang gi sog po smin rings po //
NK038(nyi)001:1381: bse khrab dmar po si li li //
NK038(nyi)001:1382: go chen 'bar ba'i go mig nas //
NK038(nyi)001:1383: khrag mda' dug mda' dgra la rgyob //
NK038(nyi)001:1384: ru skyogs nag po dgra la thun //
NK038(nyi)001:1385: yungs kar khro bo khro mor 'khrigs //
NK038(nyi)001:1386: zor gyi bdag po bskyod tsam na //
NK038(nyi)001:1388: rgya mtsho zho 'khrog chi li li //
NK038(nyi)001:1389: bse yi ging chen bskyod tsam na //
NK038(nyi)001:1390: mon gyi lus la dung seng rkang //
NK038(nyi)001:1391: lcags kyi gzhu la zangs gyi rkang //
NK038(nyi)001:1392: drag po sngags kyi shugs gyis gdung //
NK038(nyi)001:1393: bse yi lag len g.yon pa spras //
NK038(nyi)001:1394: mon gyi dug mda' nag po la //
NK038(nyi)001:1395: nyi zla khyung dang 'ug pa khra //
NK038(nyi)001:1396: gzer chen 'bebs pa'i gshog pa can //
NK038(nyi)001:1397: gnod sbyin bye ba sa yar bcas //
NK038(nyi)001:1398: nam gyi phar phyed tshur phyed na //
NK038(nyi)001:1399: ma mo tshogs kyi dmag dang bcas //
NK038(nyi)001:1400: snying gi sgong pa bcad re ran //
NK038(nyi)001:1401: srog rtsa dbugs 'di gtub re ran //
NK038(nyi)001:1402: dug mda' dgra yi snying la rgyob //
NK038(nyi)001:1404: lha yi sde dpon tshogs kyi bdag /
NK038(nyi)001:1405: legs ldan nag po mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)001:1406: dur khrod bdag po sgrol ba'i ging //
NK038(nyi)001:1407: khyad par 'phags pa'i bla ma la //
NK038(nyi)001:1408: dad pa'i sems kyis rab btud nas //
NK038(nyi)001:1409: mthu med 'jig rten skyabs gsol cig /
NK038(nyi)001:1410: chos kyi srung ma dam la 'du //
NK038(nyi)001:1411: sngags kyi ma sring dam la 'du //
NK038(nyi)001:1413: mgon po nag po dmag sna drongs //
NK038(nyi)001:1415: lnga phung rtsad nas gcad pa'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)001:1416: mu stegs k+aa la'i thod pa la //
NK038(nyi)001:1417: zor gyi gzhu mchog lings se ling //
NK038(nyi)001:1418: sngags kyi rgyud sgra brengs se breng //
NK038(nyi)001:1419: rak+ta chags pa'i smyug ma la //
NK038(nyi)001:1420: gsod byed dug gi sgro yis bskyon //
NK038(nyi)001:1421: tsha dpal thun gyi rgyus kyis dkris //
NK038(nyi)001:1422: yungs kar dpal gyi made'u gsal //
NK038(nyi)001:1424: dgra yi snying la dug mda' ya //
NK038(nyi)001:1425: rnam shes rten la dug mda' ya //
NK038(nyi)001:1426: ma h+aa la dgra bo srog phrig phrig chu ma chu ma hur hur rag+mo snying rtsa breng breng /
NK038(nyi)001:1427: mar dam ma ma rag+mo cho cho ni sha ku ru b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)001:1429: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK038(nyi)001:1430: drag po gnad kyi le'u ste bcu drug pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:1431: de nas gtad khram gnan pa'i las 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:1432: sa sna bdun gyi 'dag pa la //
NK038(nyi)001:1433: tshad dang ldan pa'i mkhar byas la //
NK038(nyi)001:1434: nang du legs ldan sku gzugs rten //
NK038(nyi)001:1435: steng du las kyi bya khyung bzhag /
NK038(nyi)001:1436: dur khrod ro ras khru gang la //
NK038(nyi)001:1437: dgra bo'i dri mas byug byas la //
NK038(nyi)001:1438: sbrul nag 'khyil pa'i lte ba ru //
NK038(nyi)001:1439: dug dang khrag gis 'khor lo la //
NK038(nyi)001:1440: mu khyud bzhi ru bskor byas la //
NK038(nyi)001:1441: dbus su rtsi mar sbyar ba'i khrag /
NK038(nyi)001:1442: dmigs pa'i gzugs bri ming rus dgod //
NK038(nyi)001:1443: g.yas su gnyen po lto bar klu //
NK038(nyi)001:1444: rgyab tu sa bdag 'doms su bse //
NK038(nyi)001:1445: 'byung po dug bzhi dmigs pas gzung //
NK038(nyi)001:1446: de phyis sngags rim 'di dag ni //
NK038(nyi)001:1447: yig mgo nang du bstan la bri //
NK038(nyi)001:1448: n+aa ga du n+aa ga du he la he la 'dus 'dus //
NK038(nyi)001:1449: a kro t+ai shwa r+ai n+aa ga rag+mo he zhu la phos phos shig shig /
NK038(nyi)001:1451: klu mo'i tshogs he zhen hu zhen n+aa ga zhen dbugs la thum thum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK038(nyi)001:1452: klu srin sdud de dam med 'khril //
NK038(nyi)001:1453: de mthar dug dang khrag sbyar la //
NK038(nyi)001:1454: sngags 'di bris la ming byang spel //
NK038(nyi)001:1455: n+aa ga du n+aa ga du he la he //
NK038(nyi)001:1456: 'dus 'dus nag po bam tsi tse rgyal //
NK038(nyi)001:1457: drag thur snying la 'dus myags myags rtsa bzhi skums //
NK038(nyi)001:1459: thur thur sod n+aa ga gur ling snying la 'dus 'dus /
NK038(nyi)001:1460: n+ri long n+ri sod sa ma ya dam dam dza
NK038(nyi)001:1461: dza n+aa ga rak+sha che ge mo kha kha kh+aa
NK038(nyi)001:1462: hi // de mthar ma h+aa k+aa la yi //
NK038(nyi)001:1463: bsnyen bsgrub bas da thun nang bstan bri //
NK038(nyi)001:1464: lha chen mgon po nag po ni //
NK038(nyi)001:1465: 'chi bdag klu yi ded dpon yin //
NK038(nyi)001:1466: 'khor lo dril nas kan m+aa ra ya /
NK038(nyi)001:1467: ku ku ka yi su bu ru //
NK038(nyi)001:1468: tsi ta dz+wa la'i thod pa ru //
NK038(nyi)001:1469: ma 'tshor khro chu'i rgyas gdab nas //
NK038(nyi)001:1470: mun pa nag po'i klong du dril //
NK038(nyi)001:1471: dkar nag sbrul gyi thag pas bsdam //
NK038(nyi)001:1472: nag po gdol ba'i srang na yang //
NK038(nyi)001:1473: mda' gang bcal bar dong 'brus la //
NK038(nyi)001:1474: phyogs bzhi mchog gi phur pa bzhi //
NK038(nyi)001:1475: gshin rje gshed dang rta mgrin dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1476: gsang bdag nyid kyi sprul bar bsgom //
NK038(nyi)001:1477: rang nyid mgon po nag por bsgom //
NK038(nyi)001:1478: nag gsum khrag dang gla rtsi dug /
NK038(nyi)001:1479: dri spos sbyar la lus la gnas //
NK038(nyi)001:1480: lha srin kun la gser skyems gtang //
NK038(nyi)001:1481: rten bdag de la rtsi sman sbyar //
NK038(nyi)001:1482: thod pa nang du bcug nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:1483: snying po de gnyis brgya brgya bzlas //
NK038(nyi)001:1484: mngas na klu srin rang la 'du //
NK038(nyi)001:1485: de steng khams gsum klu rnams kun //
NK038(nyi)001:1486: mo rnams chags pa'i tshul gyis 'du //
NK038(nyi)001:1487: pho rnams rngam pa'i zas su za //
NK038(nyi)001:1488: khro bo'i mkhar dang khyung gis gnan //
NK038(nyi)001:1489: dur sol rgya gram steng nas dgab //
NK038(nyi)001:1490: nyi shu rtsa gcig phyir bskyed la //
NK038(nyi)001:1491: tho gzug rgyal ba'i dal du bsgom //
NK038(nyi)001:1492: bskor ba phyin ka log tu bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1493: dug gi sgro ba gtan par dru //
NK038(nyi)001:1494: dug khrag snyigs pas rjes gcod bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1495: slar log tshogs mchod bkra shis bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1496: des ni lam la the tshom med //
NK038(nyi)001:1498: dpal mgon po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las //
NK038(nyi)001:1499: gtad khram gnan pa'i las bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu bdun pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:1500: de nas drag po gshin rje ltar sgrub pa 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:1501: dang po gdeng ldan sngags pa yis //
NK038(nyi)001:1502: dur khrod chen po rab 'jigs pa'i //
NK038(nyi)001:1503: nags ri tsher ma rab tu rtsub //
NK038(nyi)001:1504: gdug pa'i tshogs su lha srin yod //
NK038(nyi)001:1505: sngar shi mi ro sbubs pa'i gnas //
NK038(nyi)001:1506: dug dang mtshon cha'i thun sgrub ni //
NK038(nyi)001:1507: tha chung bzhi yi mar ngo la //
NK038(nyi)001:1508: sngon 'gro las kun rdzogs byas nas //
NK038(nyi)001:1509: dur khrod gnas su man+dala ni /
NK038(nyi)001:1510: 'dom gang gru bzhi chag chag gdab //
NK038(nyi)001:1511: rabs chad phung khyim grib sa la //
NK038(nyi)001:1512: 'brub khung lcags khang rtse gsum bran //
NK038(nyi)001:1513: rtsang dang thod phreng me ri bri //
NK038(nyi)001:1514: dug khrag dur sol sbyar byugs la //
NK038(nyi)001:1515: dbus su mon thod ja ril du //
NK038(nyi)001:1516: srub ma'i lo ma zhing chen ras //
NK038(nyi)001:1517: skyin thang chu shul rngu cho phub //
NK038(nyi)001:1518: gangs dum rgya mtsho'i lbu ba la //
NK038(nyi)001:1519: grog mkhar sa dang rang gi mkhar //
NK038(nyi)001:1520: dug khrag sbrus la lid+ha bri //
NK038(nyi)001:1521: kan d+ha'i shing la dug khrag gis //
NK038(nyi)001:1522: ming rus lo khams khram sngags bri //
NK038(nyi)001:1523: sngo dmar phur pa ske nas gdags //
NK038(nyi)001:1524: rgya tshil gu gul dud pas bdug /
NK038(nyi)001:1525: lcags phur drug gis ngar blud la //
NK038(nyi)001:1526: 'chi bdag gshin rjer bsgoms la gtad //
