NK038(nyi)001:1527: gri thog dam dmar thod sme bar //
NK038(nyi)001:1528: ra dug re'u lcag spyang dug dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1529: btsan dug ba spru thar nu thug /
NK038(nyi)001:1530: mi rta byi ba gar yi khrag /
NK038(nyi)001:1531: gcan gzan mche sder mtshon cha'i dpal //
NK038(nyi)001:1532: lcags rgod zangs rgod rdo phye sbyar //
NK038(nyi)001:1533: gu gul nag po'i tsha ba sbyar //
NK038(nyi)001:1534: chang gis sbyar la dar sna gdags //
NK038(nyi)001:1535: lcags sam thod pa'i snod nang du //
NK038(nyi)001:1536: dpal bshos khru gang rak+tasa brgyan //
NK038(nyi)001:1537: nag gsum khrag dang snying gis brgyan //
NK038(nyi)001:1538: thod par bshos bu gru gsum dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1539: gru bzhi mkhar thabs zung gsum bcu //
NK038(nyi)001:1540: rta nag ra dkar khram gyi snying //
NK038(nyi)001:1541: ra rgya'i ban khrag brgyan pa bzhag /
NK038(nyi)001:1542: dmar gtor tshil chen sprin khebs can //
NK038(nyi)001:1543: dkar gtor rtsi sman klu la bsham //
NK038(nyi)001:1544: phyogs bzhir mchod pa'i bye brag tshogs //
NK038(nyi)001:1545: gcan gzan rgyan rnams bdud lta bu //
NK038(nyi)001:1546: stong nyid ngang las gshin rje bsgom //
NK038(nyi)001:1547: b+h+r+aum las lcags khang steng shod du //
NK038(nyi)001:1548: 'od las gyur pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK038(nyi)001:1549: gzas pa'i gdan la stag chen khri //
NK038(nyi)001:1550: me dpung 'bar ba'i klong dkyil du //
NK038(nyi)001:1551: dun las yi ge bcu bzhi pa //
NK038(nyi)001:1552: 'chi bdag zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa //
NK038(nyi)001:1553: mthing nag dbu skra kham nag 'phro //
NK038(nyi)001:1554: sku la ber nag brtsegs pa gsol //
NK038(nyi)001:1555: g.yas na tsan dan bing chen la //
NK038(nyi)001:1556: g.yon pa thod pa khrag gis bkang //
NK038(nyi)001:1557: yab yum gnyis med 'khril bar bsgom //
NK038(nyi)001:1558: 'khor gyi ded dpon shan pa drug /
NK038(nyi)001:1559: kun kyang khro bo'i cha lugs can //
NK038(nyi)001:1560: smig pa'i khri la brkyang bskum bgad //
NK038(nyi)001:1561: nag po khram shing zhags pa thogs //
NK038(nyi)001:1563: nag po ban dmar mdung can 'jigs //
NK038(nyi)001:1564: ljang nag sbrul zhags sbal 'dzin klu //
NK038(nyi)001:1565: dmar skya btsan zhags mdung dmar 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)001:1566: ljang ser rdo rje snying 'dzin gying //
NK038(nyi)001:1567: phyi rol ma mo rngam pa ltar //
NK038(nyi)001:1568: rang bzhin gnas nas bkug la bstim //
NK038(nyi)001:1569: phyi nang chod pa sngags kyis dbul //
NK038(nyi)001:1571: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las //
NK038(nyi)001:1572: gshin rje'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i le'u bco brgyad pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:1573: de nas de yi rim pa yang /
NK038(nyi)001:1574: yab yum gsang ba'i srog sngags bzlas //
NK038(nyi)001:1575: bsnyen pa tshad la phebs pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1576: yab yum bar du dregs pa gzhug /
NK038(nyi)001:1577: bskul dang dmigs pa ting 'dzin gzhug thun la dmar nag yi ge ma //
NK038(nyi)001:1578: sngo nag ha dang sngo skya ca //
NK038(nyi)001:1579: sngags kyi 'od zer dregs pa'i zhal //
NK038(nyi)001:1580: thun la bstims la yi ge zhu //
NK038(nyi)001:1581: nad dug mtshon du gyur par bsgom //
NK038(nyi)001:1582: dmigs pa zhugs pa'i rtags byung na //
NK038(nyi)001:1583: drag sngags thun gyis thun du dbab //
NK038(nyi)001:1584: zhag bdun rdzogs nas phur pa gdab //
NK038(nyi)001:1585: ling+ga thod pa bcas pa de //
NK038(nyi)001:1586: ro khung mun pa'i gting ru gnan //
NK038(nyi)001:1587: nya stong drag po'i zor kha 'phang //
NK038(nyi)001:1588: de yi gsang sngags 'di dag yin //
NK038(nyi)001:1589: badz+ra yak+sha k+aa la k+aa la //
NK038(nyi)001:1590: ma h+aa g+ha na g+hu ti hri da ya //
NK038(nyi)001:1591: badz+ra ging ka ra rak+ka ka li mu ma mu
NK038(nyi)001:1592: sham khrag la mugs sham hri dzahduna ru tra ru
NK038(nyi)001:1593: thum b+ha ti r+aa dza tsa pa la a shug
NK038(nyi)001:1594: me / ma t+aa ka rag+sha nag mo ting lam ma b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)001:1595: n+aa ga hu ti sa n+aa ga ru ru ha shu la tsa tri sham dza yam /
NK038(nyi)001:1596: badz+ra sa tu tri n+aa ga dun tri /
NK038(nyi)001:1599: tsat+ta thun rmugs khrag thibs rbad /
NK038(nyi)001:1600: li shag rbad ni hur thums dzahkhrama rbad ya thum ri li li b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)001:1603: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK038(nyi)001:1604: drag po las sbyor gyi le'u ste bcu dgu pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:1605: de nas dpa' bo ging gi sgrub pa 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:1606: bstan pa spyin yi blo can gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:1607: rta mchog dbang du bsgoms nas kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:1608: mtshan ldan dur khrod gnas bzung nas //
NK038(nyi)001:1609: las bzhi tshang ba'i dkyil 'khor bri //
NK038(nyi)001:1610: tha mar dmar nag ro nyes sdam //
NK038(nyi)001:1611: dbus su thun khung thur du bru //
NK038(nyi)001:1612: nang ris gsum ldan mtshon cha rtsod //
NK038(nyi)001:1613: mi thod dug dang chang gis sbyar //
NK038(nyi)001:1614: khrag sna mche ltar mtshon dbal brdar //
NK038(nyi)001:1615: dar nag gur phub ro nyes bsdam //
NK038(nyi)001:1616: dgra sogs g.yas la dmigs pa gzugs //
NK038(nyi)001:1617: thun gyis de la brgyangs la bzhag /
NK038(nyi)001:1618: dur g.yam ro sol rgya gram bri //
NK038(nyi)001:1619: thun khung kha bcad steng du dgab //
NK038(nyi)001:1620: gri bo'i thod pa dmar chod du //
NK038(nyi)001:1621: dpa' bo'i snying dang zangs thig dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1622: srog snying bcug la dar gyis gril //
NK038(nyi)001:1623: bse phor sha sna snying sna khrag /
NK038(nyi)001:1624: rin chen 'bru yi gtor ma bsham //
NK038(nyi)001:1625: bka' sdod dpa' bo ging chen bo //
NK038(nyi)001:1626: dmar nag 'jigs pa'i bse khrab gsol //
NK038(nyi)001:1627: bse rmog gyon pa dpa' bo'i chas //
NK038(nyi)001:1628: phyag na zangs gri tsit+ta bsnams //
NK038(nyi)001:1629: 'khor ni dregs pa'i spu gri bzhi //
NK038(nyi)001:1630: srin po sa ma r+aa dza dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1631: gshin rje ya ma r+aa dza dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1632: bdud po ha nu phag sha dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1633: gnod sbyin dz+wa la garba dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1634: dkar sngo dmar dang ljang gu'i mdog /
NK038(nyi)001:1635: gri thogs tsit+ta za ba'i tshul //
NK038(nyi)001:1636: dgug cing bstims la mchod pa 'bul //
NK038(nyi)001:1637: sgo phugs med pa'i sngags 'di bzlas //
NK038(nyi)001:1638: tro ta ni tro ta ni pa tra pa tra shu la shu la d+ha sha gri ba /
NK038(nyi)001:1639: yak+sha gri ba ging kar ging ka ra ging tsa to ging tsa to /
NK038(nyi)001:1640: par ta te par ta te sha pa te sha pa te /
NK038(nyi)001:1643: snying kha rag snying kha raka /
NK038(nyi)001:1645: dgra bo'i snying la b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)001:1647: dgra bo gtor cig rtsa rtsa nan //
NK038(nyi)001:1648: na ga ro ya mi pa ri la rbad //
NK038(nyi)001:1649: ma ra ni snying la mugs //
NK038(nyi)001:1650: snying la mugs srog la rtsa ba ma //
NK038(nyi)001:1651: su ru su bam ril rbad //
NK038(nyi)001:1652: drag po gnad kyi gsang sngags 'di //
NK038(nyi)001:1653: dam can nye snying las la 'dzud //
NK038(nyi)001:1655: dmigs pa bkug bstim nad rlangs kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:1656: bu ga dgu nas thim zhing gsod //
NK038(nyi)001:1657: 'bum phrag bzlas pas the tshom med //
NK038(nyi)001:1658: a ba lo ki te ya na ma sho hri ti snying kha la rag sha /
NK038(nyi)001:1659: khas blangs sa ma ya thum thum //
NK038(nyi)001:1660: ru lu ru lu ma he b+h+yo //
NK038(nyi)001:1661: nad dang thun gyis byin brlab 'di //
NK038(nyi)001:1662: brgya ba'i bar du bcu bcu sbrel //
NK038(nyi)001:1663: gsang sngags mtshon cha 'di nyid gdags //
NK038(nyi)001:1666: a ka ni rbad tri ka la sa ma ya h+aum b+h+yo /
NK038(nyi)001:1667: dral dral snying snying la dral //
NK038(nyi)001:1671: tshal pa tshal ba rbad rbad /
NK038(nyi)001:1672: zhag grangs bcu gsum tshang ba dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1673: lid+ga gsum du gtum byas te //
NK038(nyi)001:1674: gcig la thun brab gcig ni bsreg /
NK038(nyi)001:1675: gcig ni dur mched gsum la gtad //
NK038(nyi)001:1676: ki kang drag po rgyu ba la //
NK038(nyi)001:1677: thun khrag dgra la zor du 'phang //
NK038(nyi)001:1678: ging sgrub drag pos gsang sngags 'di //
NK038(nyi)001:1679: nus min spyad na rang la ngan //
NK038(nyi)001:1680: des na rab tu basngagasa te ska //
NK038(nyi)001:1682: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK038(nyi)001:1683: dpa' bo ging sgrub kyi le'u ste nyi shu pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:1684: de nas sgrub pa'i rtags kyi rim pa 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:1686: sgrub po mkha' la 'phur ba dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1687: sa la mi thogs chur mi 'bying //
NK038(nyi)001:1688: legs ldan mdun du ci bya zer //
NK038(nyi)001:1689: rabs kyi rtags su shes par bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1690: phung po me 'bar mda' la sgra //
NK038(nyi)001:1691: sman phud khol zhing rak+ta lud //
NK038(nyi)001:1694: yams dang nad kyi na bun 'thul //
NK038(nyi)001:1697: tha ma rmi lam ston par 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:1698: dgra bcom tshogs su 'ong ba dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1699: ban+de nag po mon pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1701: g.yag khyu khyi nag bya nag dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1702: mchod rten nag po me stag 'phro //
NK038(nyi)001:1703: skar mda' mang po lhung bar 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:1704: bsnyen nas nye ba'i rtags su shes //
NK038(nyi)001:1705: go tshol mtshon cha mang po brdung ba dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1707: las la tshud pa'i mtshan ma yin //
NK038(nyi)001:1708: gzhan yang gshin rje sgrub pa la //
NK038(nyi)001:1709: mon dang ban+de tshub ma g.yag /
NK038(nyi)001:1710: btsan btsun stag seng lha khang 'od //
NK038(nyi)001:1711: bud med dre'u nag chu rlung 'byung //
NK038(nyi)001:1712: nya sbrul klu yi cho 'phrul ston //
NK038(nyi)001:1713: mi rta dmar po me dang 'od //
NK038(nyi)001:1714: khra spyang ban de tshong pa 'byung //
NK038(nyi)001:1716: bya yis bya la 'debs pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1719: sha la longs spyod god la rol //
NK038(nyi)001:1720: brag chen rtsad nas bton pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1721: gdung brgyud rtsad nas gcod pa nges //
NK038(nyi)001:1722: sdong po bcad na dgra nyid 'chi //
NK038(nyi)001:1723: yal ga bcad na 'gab la ngan //
NK038(nyi)001:1724: don po bsad cing snying phyung na //
NK038(nyi)001:1725: the tshom med pa'i rtags yin no //
NK038(nyi)001:1726: rgyan 'phrog gos bshus grogs la ngan //
NK038(nyi)001:1727: nag po ldog pa'i mtshan ma ni //
NK038(nyi)001:1728: mun pa sros dang mdze pho rgol //
NK038(nyi)001:1729: g.yag rgod rdung zhing gcan gzan rmug /
NK038(nyi)001:1730: chu sna ldog pa khros par shes //
NK038(nyi)001:1731: mul dang sprang long longs spyod 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)001:1733: gzhan yang nyes legs las rnams ston //
NK038(nyi)001:1734: cis kyang las 'gyangs ldog gyur na //
NK038(nyi)001:1735: kan+d+ha'i shing la mgon po'i gzugs //
NK038(nyi)001:1736: mtho gang tshad las skye mched rdzogs //
NK038(nyi)001:1737: spyi bor ru lu bzlog pa bri //
NK038(nyi)001:1738: lag pa g.yas g.yon bsnyen sngags gnyis //
NK038(nyi)001:1739: rkang ba sgrub dang bsad pa'o //
NK038(nyi)001:1740: thun sngags kho rang lus la bri //
NK038(nyi)001:1741: de la dgug cing bstims byas la //
NK038(nyi)001:1742: zhag gsum dpal gtor 'og tu gzir //
NK038(nyi)001:1743: bsnyen sgrub sngags la las bzlog brdeg /
NK038(nyi)001:1744: drag shul 'byung po'i nyi ma la //
NK038(nyi)001:1745: ral gri phyar la gnyen pos brdeg /
NK038(nyi)001:1746: dug shing gdug pa'i me yis bsreg /
NK038(nyi)001:1747: bka' rten sa dang thal ba sbyar //
NK038(nyi)001:1748: gzugs bya khog par ling+ga gzhug /
NK038(nyi)001:1749: bdud rtsi gtor ma mchod pa bstab //
NK038(nyi)001:1750: dur khrod dbus su dong brus la //
NK038(nyi)001:1751: mgon po'i gzugs gzhug dur g.yam dgab //
NK038(nyi)001:1752: mchod rten nag po khru gang la //
NK038(nyi)001:1753: gu gul dud pas bdug la gnan //
NK038(nyi)001:1754: lha nyid gnad la dbab pa'i las //
NK038(nyi)001:1755: ya bag shar rab tu gsang //
NK038(nyi)001:1757: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las //
NK038(nyi)001:1758: grub rtags kyi le'u ste nyi shu rtsa gcig pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:1759: de nas dbang gi rim pa 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:1760: nyams dga' byed pa'i sa phyogs su //
NK038(nyi)001:1761: man+dala byas la me tog dgram //
NK038(nyi)001:1762: gtor ma mchod pa'i rdzas kun dgram //
NK038(nyi)001:1763: rin chen bum pa mdzes pa la //
NK038(nyi)001:1764: kha rgyan mgul chings ldan par bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1765: sna tshogs dri dang rin po che //
NK038(nyi)001:1766: snying bo 'bru sna chu yis dgang //
NK038(nyi)001:1767: nang du mgon po'i dkyil 'khor bskyed //
NK038(nyi)001:1768: mchod pa'i rdzas kun tshang ba dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1769: slob mas nor rdzas yon phul la //
NK038(nyi)001:1771: dpal mgon nag po ye shes sku //
NK038(nyi)001:1772: lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK038(nyi)001:1774: dpa' bo thugs rjes gzung bar mdzod //
NK038(nyi)001:1775: de skad gsol pa lan bzhi gdab //
NK038(nyi)001:1781: gnas skabs bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)001:1783: slob mas nus par khas blangs shing //
NK038(nyi)001:1784: sdom pa rim par blang bar bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1785: chos kun rang bzhin dag pas na //
NK038(nyi)001:1786: bdag kyang rang bzhin rnams par dag /
NK038(nyi)001:1787: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK038(nyi)001:1788: thugs dam da byings mchog rnam dag cing //
NK038(nyi)001:1789: sems can 'byam klas ma lus kun //
NK038(nyi)001:1790: mchog nyid sgrub par sbyor bas na //
NK038(nyi)001:1791: rgyal ba rgya mtsho kun 'dus pas //
NK038(nyi)001:1792: sku yi dbyig tu bdag skyed cig /
NK038(nyi)001:1793: ye shes rin chen dbu rgyan can //
NK038(nyi)001:1794: gzi brjid phung po bla na med //
NK038(nyi)001:1795: sangs rgyas rin chen 'byung ba yis /
NK038(nyi)001:1796: rnam par rgyal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK038(nyi)001:1797: dbyig gi ye shes gtso mchog nyid //
NK038(nyi)001:1798: rdo rje dam pa mchog 'dzin pa //
NK038(nyi)001:1799: khyod ni dam tshig gtso lags kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:1800: dbang phyug rgyal por dbang bskur ro //
NK038(nyi)001:1801: bcom ldan thams cad mchog ni bdag lags te //
NK038(nyi)001:1802: mchog nyid sgrub phyir rdo rje blang bar bgyi //
NK038(nyi)001:1803: rdo rje rgyal po khyod bzhugs pas //
NK038(nyi)001:1804: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje ste //
NK038(nyi)001:1805: rdo rje dam tshig mchog nyid kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:1806: phun sum tshogs pa sgrub bar bgyi /
NK038(nyi)001:1807: chos kun rdo rje'i mtshan nyid de //
NK038(nyi)001:1808: rdo rje la yang mtshan nyid med //
NK038(nyi)001:1809: rdo rje lta bu'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK038(nyi)001:1810: don kun rdo rje lta bur gsol //
NK038(nyi)001:1811: 'di ni sangs rgyas gsungs dbyings nyid //
NK038(nyi)001:1812: ye shes sems dpa'i dam tshig rnams //
NK038(nyi)001:1813: rdo rje sems dpa'i dka' thub dam //
NK038(nyi)001:1814: rtag tu bdag gis bcangs par bgyi //
NK038(nyi)001:1815: brgya ba'i tshul gyis sgrib pa sbyang //
NK038(nyi)001:1816: mgon po'i gzhung bsrang bsnyen par bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1817: de nas 'jug pa'i cho ga bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1819: rdo rje chos dbyings kun gyi gtso //
NK038(nyi)001:1820: mi rnams chags pa chen po ste //
NK038(nyi)001:1821: ma lus kun gyi 'byung gnas mchog /
NK038(nyi)001:1822: bde ba mchog gi dam pa lags //
NK038(nyi)001:1823: khyod ni dam tshig kun gyi gtso //
NK038(nyi)001:1824: rdo rje sems dpa' skyed mdzad pa //
NK038(nyi)001:1825: sems can don grub phrin las mdzod //
NK038(nyi)001:1826: thugs rjes mnyam sbyor grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)001:1827: sangs rgyas yon tan 'byung pa'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)001:1828: rdo rje rin chen bla na med //
NK038(nyi)001:1829: rdo rje chos kyi glu blang pas //
NK038(nyi)001:1830: las kyi rdo rje khyed par 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:1831: h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa badz+ra d+ha dz+wa la man+da
NK038(nyi)001:1832: la phata phata ha la ha la ram kro d+ha
NK038(nyi)001:1833: yam tig sna kham ta kem ta kem phata /
NK038(nyi)001:1835: i dan te na ra kan ba ra hri da yam /
NK038(nyi)001:1838: sid+d+hi bi na badz+ra a mri ta kro d+ha kan /
NK038(nyi)001:1839: sngon tshe gong nas 'phel pa yi //
NK038(nyi)001:1840: bdag gi nye gnas gang lags pa'i //
NK038(nyi)001:1841: las kyi 'phro dang thugs rje'i lha //
NK038(nyi)001:1842: da lta nyid du babs gyur cig /
NK038(nyi)001:1843: h+aum h+aum gu h+ya badz+ra tsit+ta h+aum //
NK038(nyi)001:1844: ni ye shes lhun gyis grub //
NK038(nyi)001:1845: mu ni ye nas rang sangs rgyas //
NK038(nyi)001:1846: h+aum ni rtsa ba byang chub sems //
NK038(nyi)001:1847: dkyil 'khor rnams gsum dbyer med pas //
NK038(nyi)001:1848: ha zhes mthong bas yongs su dag /
NK038(nyi)001:1849: ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs par mthong //
NK038(nyi)001:1850: rdo rje zhes su ming btags nas //
NK038(nyi)001:1851: rdo rje theg pa'i gsang sgor bzhag /
NK038(nyi)001:1852: h+aum mkha' dbyings rnam dag bum pa chen po na //
NK038(nyi)001:1853: dbal ldan mgon po'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs par bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)001:1854: gnyis med ye shes byang chub sems rtags chus //
NK038(nyi)001:1855: dri ma kun sbyangs khams gsum zil gyis gnan //
NK038(nyi)001:1856: byin brlabs mthu yis dbang rdzogs thob par shog /
NK038(nyi)001:1857: b+hur kur ma h+aa k+aa la ma h+aa la /
NK038(nyi)001:1859: dngos sam bdud rtsi bum pa la //
NK038(nyi)001:1860: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gyi //
NK038(nyi)001:1861: byang chub sems kyi bde ba bzhin //
NK038(nyi)001:1863: dkyil 'khor rnam gsum dbyer med don //
NK038(nyi)001:1864: yab yum gnyis med bde ba'i don //
NK038(nyi)001:1865: byang chub sems kyi thig le 'dis //
NK038(nyi)001:1866: bde chen thabs kyi rgyal por dbang bskur ro //
NK038(nyi)001:1867: badz+ra a mri ta a ti sarba man tra tha /
NK038(nyi)001:1868: de nas bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)001:1869: drag po'i rdzas rnams thams cad la //
NK038(nyi)001:1870: mgon po 'khor bcas bskyed bstims la //
NK038(nyi)001:1871: yon tan brjod la sbyin par bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1872: bsnyen sgrub rim pa'i sngags brjod cing //
NK038(nyi)001:1873: man ngag thams cad sbyin par bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1874: des ni ci bsam 'grub pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1875: rig 'dzin sa la smin pa yin //
NK038(nyi)001:1877: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK038(nyi)001:1878: 'bang bsgyur ba'i le'u ste nyer gnyis pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:1879: des nas dam tshig gi rim pa 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:1880: dam tshig la yang rnam gnyis te //
NK038(nyi)001:1881: rtsa ba gsum dang yan lag gnyis //
NK038(nyi)001:1882: rdo rje slob dpon mig gi 'bras //
NK038(nyi)001:1884: mi shes rmongs pa'i blo gros mkhan //
NK038(nyi)001:1885: lam stor rnams kyi sa mkhan mig /
NK038(nyi)001:1886: gdung ba sel ba'i rin po che //
NK038(nyi)001:1887: yid bzhin nor bu lta bur gzung //
NK038(nyi)001:1888: de la 'gal ba rdul dang bral //
NK038(nyi)001:1889: rang byung ye shes yi dam lha //
NK038(nyi)001:1890: mun khung sel ba'i mig bzhin gzung //
NK038(nyi)001:1891: chu bo gal du gsad mi bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1892: spyi gsang ba dang bar gsang ba //
NK038(nyi)001:1893: gnyer gtad pa dang 'os pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1894: skye bo'i tshogs la dben par bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1895: yan lag blta ba sdom pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1896: spyod pa rgyun gyi dam tshig go //
NK038(nyi)001:1897: nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:1898: mi skye mi 'gag ngo bor blta //
NK038(nyi)001:1899: phag rgod lta bu'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:1900: gtsang sme re dogs mi blta bar //
NK038(nyi)001:1901: mun khung dug gis gser 'gyur bzhin //
NK038(nyi)001:1902: rnam rtog ye shes chen por blta //
NK038(nyi)001:1903: seng ge rtsal rdzogs ji bzhin du //
NK038(nyi)001:1904: ma bgrod sa rnams non par blta //
NK038(nyi)001:1905: de phyir blta ba'i dam tshig bzhi //
NK038(nyi)001:1906: rang byung sems kyi bye brag yin //
NK038(nyi)001:1907: spyod pa rgyun gyi dam tshig drug /
NK038(nyi)001:1908: dus kyi spyod lam ji bzhin du //
NK038(nyi)001:1909: gsang ba'i lam min gzhan mi 'gro //
NK038(nyi)001:1910: rig ba'i bdag min phyag mi btsal //
NK038(nyi)001:1911: mi smra bar ni sha chen bsnyen //
NK038(nyi)001:1912: bstan pa spyi yi sku dgra la //
NK038(nyi)001:1913: byams shing gdung pa'i spyod pa spangs //
NK038(nyi)001:1914: rang bzhin zhe sdang ldang mi dgos //
NK038(nyi)001:1915: mi dge mtshams med la sogs spangs //
NK038(nyi)001:1916: gzhan yang sngags rdo rje dang //
NK038(nyi)001:1917: bkod pa'i rtsa ba rang bzhin bsrung //

NK038(nyi)001:1929: byams dang snying rje sngon btang la //

NK038(nyi)001:1961: rta dang glang po ba glang 'bru //

NK038(nyi)001:1977: gzhan yang gong gi rdzas bkod rnams //

NK038(nyi)001:1979: zho chang kha zas gnod la 'dug /

NK038(nyi)001:1981: mi phyugs srung ba ske ru gdags //

NK038(nyi)001:1984: dri spos sbyar la lus la byug /
NK038(nyi)001:1985: sman dang ba dmar 'o ma la //
NK038(nyi)001:1986: basngagasa la khong du gtang bar bya //
NK038(nyi)001:1987: bsnyen pa rdzas dgod dud pas bdug /
NK038(nyi)001:1988: drag po'i sngags kyi dbal gyis bskrad //
NK038(nyi)001:1989: sri'u rin chen rnam lnga la //
NK038(nyi)001:1990: sman sna lnga la sbyar la gdab //
NK038(nyi)001:1991: rtsa ba khyad par sngags gsum la //

NK038(nyi)001:1995: ha na ha na da ha da ha /

NK038(nyi)001:2003: dbang chen stobs kyi sbyor ba 'di la //

NK038(nyi)001:2005: rgyal sa zin pa'i mkhar sa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2006: chos srid thob pa'i khri stegs dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2007: btsun mo mtshan ldan ma la gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:2008: bka' rten dri can dur khrod kyi //

NK038(nyi)001:2010: 'brub khung khru gang zla gam bkod //

NK038(nyi)001:2012: rgyal blon stobs dang mu stegs dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2013: bgegs chen gcan gzan gdug pa'i sa //
NK038(nyi)001:2014: rdzas la gzugs bya ming byang dgod //
NK038(nyi)001:2015: thod pa srubs med nang du gzhugs //
NK038(nyi)001:2016: 'brub khung nang du de bcug la //
NK038(nyi)001:2017: bsnyen sgrub sngags gsum dril ba la //
NK038(nyi)001:2018: dbang du bsdu ba'i sngags 'di bzlas //
NK038(nyi)001:2019: ma h+aa k+aa la p+aa sham ku hrim hri pa sha ma na ya hring hring dzah dzah /
NK038(nyi)001:2021: bdag nyid mgon po legs ldan che //

NK038(nyi)001:2023: lcags kyu zhags pa dmar po ldog /
NK038(nyi)001:2024: thugs kar h+aum las sngags kyi mdog /
NK038(nyi)001:2025: gang la byas pa rten la phab //
NK038(nyi)001:2026: dbang chen dbang gi 'od kyis bkug /
NK038(nyi)001:2027: khab len rdo la lcags 'du ltar //
NK038(nyi)001:2028: thams cad dbang du 'dus par bsam //
NK038(nyi)001:2029: shing thog go la star bu dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2030: rgun 'brum me tog dmar po dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2031: sha khrag gsar ba'i gtor ma 'bul //
NK038(nyi)001:2032: tshil chen mngal khrag rgya skyegs dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2033: tsan dan dkar dmar g+hi wang dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2034: bse zho bag tsam ling+gara byug /
NK038(nyi)001:2035: seng ldeng me la bsro zhing bzlas //
NK038(nyi)001:2036: thon nas thod pa dar nag gril //
NK038(nyi)001:2037: rang gi mal 'og dag tu sbas //
NK038(nyi)001:2038: sngags kyi tshad ma 'bum tsho drug /
NK038(nyi)001:2040: rgyal blon stoms can gdug pa yang //
NK038(nyi)001:2041: ji ltar bsgo ba'i bka' rnams nyan //
NK038(nyi)001:2042: khams gsum mdzes ldan phyag rgya ma //
NK038(nyi)001:2044: rbod gtong spe bgegs gnod chen kun //
NK038(nyi)001:2045: ji ltar bsgo ba bran bzhin byed //
NK038(nyi)001:2046: mche sder r+aa can lce dug spos //
NK038(nyi)001:2048: 'bru dang rin chen zas bcud la //
NK038(nyi)001:2049: gong bzhin sbyar kyin bsgrub byas na //
NK038(nyi)001:2050: snang srid zas nor bdag la 'du //
NK038(nyi)001:2051: kun sdud dbang gi sbyor ba bshad //
NK038(nyi)001:2052: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las //
NK038(nyi)001:2053: dbang sdud thabs kyi le'u ste nyer lnga pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:2054: de nas dbab bsad kyi las 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:2055: drag po'i gsang sngags bar ba yang //
NK038(nyi)001:2056: gang gi 'brub khung nang du shis //
NK038(nyi)001:2057: kan d+ha'i shing la 'khor lo bri //
NK038(nyi)001:2058: dbus su yul zhing ser srung lha //
NK038(nyi)001:2059: mu khyud 'khor lo dang por bri //
NK038(nyi)001:2060: rtsibs bzhi dregs pa'i snying po bri //
NK038(nyi)001:2061: tha ma chu ris zlum po la //
NK038(nyi)001:2062: srin po ming sring dbab sngags dgod //
NK038(nyi)001:2063: yul gyi rdzas dang gnyan ra'i chu //
NK038(nyi)001:2064: byug sa la thod pa'i nang du gzhug /
NK038(nyi)001:2065: dug khrag 'bru zlum sbyar ba'i khrag /
NK038(nyi)001:2066: gong gi rdzas dang sbyar la bya //
NK038(nyi)001:2067: zhag grangs nyi shu rtsa gcig tu //
NK038(nyi)001:2068: drag po'i sngags dril ting 'dzin gsal //
NK038(nyi)001:2069: bcu gcig rdzogs nas thun brabs la //
NK038(nyi)001:2070: klu la rta gzhug zor 'phang bskul //
NK038(nyi)001:2071: de yi gsang sngags 'di dag yin //
NK038(nyi)001:2072: b+hu ru ku ru i phyi uts+tshasa ma kro d+ha h+aum phata /

NK038(nyi)001:2074: yak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya phrom phob /
NK038(nyi)001:2075: raka sha dz+wa la sa ma ya phrom phob //
NK038(nyi)001:2076: tsid tra dza la sa ma ya phrom phob //
NK038(nyi)001:2077: badz+ra rag sha sa ma ya snying ya ma khrag
NK038(nyi)001:2078: r+aa hu la phrmo phrmo hri la hri la shar
NK038(nyi)001:2079: shar / m+aa ra ya rtsa sha thibs ru sing tram hril /
NK038(nyi)001:2081: yul khams brlag par the tshom med //
NK038(nyi)001:2082: gzhan yang khram thod gsal ba la //
NK038(nyi)001:2083: mon tshil rta dang zangs lcags rgod //
NK038(nyi)001:2084: gri lcags thog lcags gser dngul dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2085: chang gis sbyar la sngags 'di bzlas //
NK038(nyi)001:2087: me dang lcags kyi gza' skar la //

NK038(nyi)001:2089: de yi gsang sngags 'di dag yin //

NK038(nyi)001:2098: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las //

NK038(nyi)001:2100: de nas gnyen po lha'i thugs dam bskul ba 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:2102: khro bo'i rgyal po gdog drug h+aum sgra can //
NK038(nyi)001:2103: yan lag drug ldan khro bo gshin rje gshed //
NK038(nyi)001:2104: ye shes rgyan gyis ma rig mun pa sel //
NK038(nyi)001:2105: gtum chen gshin rje 'joms la phyag 'tshal lo //

NK038(nyi)001:2107: dregs can stobs gzhom zil gyis mnan pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2108: ma mo mkha' 'gro rnams la dbang bsgyur nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2109: nad gtong srin po'i tshogs rnams thal bar rlogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2110: khyod kyi thugs rdzes bdag la byin gyis rlobs //

NK038(nyi)001:2112: chos rje 'od dpag med pa rdo rje'i thugs //
NK038(nyi)001:2113: spyan ras gzigs dbang h+r+ai las rngam chen sku //
NK038(nyi)001:2114: ngag gi dbang phyug rta gdong zhabs kyis gnon //
NK038(nyi)001:2115: rdo rje rta yi rta dbu yis //
NK038(nyi)001:2117: 'jig rten dregs pa gtum pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2118: rdo rje rtog pa bya sgron gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:2119: snang mdzad ngag gi dbang phyug sku //
NK038(nyi)001:2120: byang chub chen po cang shes gtso //
NK038(nyi)001:2121: lha chen dgu yi cho 'phrul gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:2122: rdo rje rta gdong sprul pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2123: nam mkha'i khams rnams gang bar mdzod //
NK038(nyi)001:2124: 'khor ba ma grol bar du ni //
NK038(nyi)001:2125: snying rje'i go cha ma bsnyel bar //
NK038(nyi)001:2126: 'khor ba'i so mtha' chod par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)001:2128: rgyal ba kun gyi gsang 'dzin pa //
NK038(nyi)001:2129: thugs rje kun gyi bdag po rdo rje 'dzin //
NK038(nyi)001:2130: drag po brtul zhugs chen po can //
NK038(nyi)001:2131: dpa' bo 'jig rten gsum las rgyal //
NK038(nyi)001:2132: sngon gyi go cha chen po yis //
NK038(nyi)001:2133: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:2134: gdul dka' ma lus 'dul mdzad pa //
NK038(nyi)001:2135: bdud kyi bdud ste bdud rnams 'joms //
NK038(nyi)001:2136: sems dpa' chen po 'bar ba'i sku //
NK038(nyi)001:2137: 'jigs su rung ba'i dpa' byad can //
NK038(nyi)001:2138: h+aum rngam 'khrug pa'i nga ro yis //
NK038(nyi)001:2139: dur khrod bdag po rab tu bcom //
NK038(nyi)001:2141: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK038(nyi)001:2142: gnyen po lha'i thugs rje bskul pa'i le'u ste nyer bdun pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:2143: de nas chos skyong bskul ba 'di gsungs so /
NK038(nyi)001:2145: nyi ma lho nub pha gi na //
NK038(nyi)001:2146: srin yul pu rangs nag po'i dkyil //
NK038(nyi)001:2147: lang ka yul gyi grong rdal na //
NK038(nyi)001:2148: ko ka thang dmar rgya mtsho yi //
NK038(nyi)001:2149: dbus na ri bo ma la ya //
NK038(nyi)001:2150: drag shul byan lag 'phyongs kyi ri //
NK038(nyi)001:2151: gnam lcags yod pa'i rtse mo na //
NK038(nyi)001:2152: chos 'dzin rigs kyi sgrub gnas te //
NK038(nyi)001:2153: rdo rje thabs kyis blta ba'i yul //
NK038(nyi)001:2154: gsur chen dud pa sprin du gtibs //
NK038(nyi)001:2155: gnam lcags chu ser mtsho ru 'khyil //
NK038(nyi)001:2156: sha rus phung bo ri ltar spungs //
NK038(nyi)001:2157: ce spyang lings su rgyug cing 'dral //
NK038(nyi)001:2158: bya gcan mang po 'phur zhing lding //
NK038(nyi)001:2160: rab tu 'jigs pa'i yul mkhar na //
NK038(nyi)001:2161: 'jigs pa'i thod mkhar ldem se ldem //
NK038(nyi)001:2162: shar phyogs bam ril stag thod mkhar //
NK038(nyi)001:2163: stag thod 'dzum mdangs mu lu lu //
NK038(nyi)001:2164: lho phyogs bam ril mi thod brtsigs //
NK038(nyi)001:2165: mi thod spyugs pa tse re re //
NK038(nyi)001:2166: nub phyogs bam ril rta thod brtsegs //
NK038(nyi)001:2167: rta thod mtsher dar lhangs se lhang //
NK038(nyi)001:2168: byang phyogs bam rim thod mkhar brtsigs //
NK038(nyi)001:2169: bya thod tsheg sgra di ri ri //
NK038(nyi)001:2170: srin po thod pa'i kha bad can //
NK038(nyi)001:2172: ngos la nga rgyal glog dmar 'khyug /
NK038(nyi)001:2173: rtse la bdud bya nag po lding //
NK038(nyi)001:2174: ru mtshon nag po pu ru ru //
NK038(nyi)001:2175: gnam lcags 'bar ba'i sgo mo gsal //
NK038(nyi)001:2176: 'jigs pa'i sku mkhar nang shed na //
NK038(nyi)001:2177: rta ro mang po gcal du bkram //
NK038(nyi)001:2178: mi ro mang po khri ru brtsigs //
NK038(nyi)001:2179: mi ro rta ro'i gdan steng na //
NK038(nyi)001:2180: mnga' bdag bdud kyi rgyal po bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)001:2181: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje yis //
NK038(nyi)001:2182: phrin las drag pos dbang bskur ba //
NK038(nyi)001:2183: sku mdog dbus zhal ljang nag brjid //
NK038(nyi)001:2184: zhal gsum 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK038(nyi)001:2185: g.yas ser thug rjes 'gro la skyobs //
NK038(nyi)001:2186: g.yon dmar chags pas dbang sdud 'gugs //
NK038(nyi)001:2187: dmar nag ral pa srid rtser 'bar //
NK038(nyi)001:2188: ral pa 'khrugs pa'i skra gseb na //
NK038(nyi)001:2189: gnam lcags thog ser skar mda' 'phro //
NK038(nyi)001:2191: nad kyi rkyal pa tshub mar 'tshub //
NK038(nyi)001:2192: zhal gdangs dbang gi mche ba gtsigs //
NK038(nyi)001:2193: rngam pa'i nga ro 'brug ltar sgrogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2194: drag po'i rkan sgra bdud ltar rdeb //
NK038(nyi)001:2196: gdug pa'i mtshon cha ma lus 'phro //
NK038(nyi)001:2197: drag po'i phyag drug gdengs pa la //
NK038(nyi)001:2198: g.yas kyi dang po gsal shing gis //
NK038(nyi)001:2199: srid pa gsum yang dbang du sdud //
NK038(nyi)001:2200: bar pa rdo rje gsor zhing 'phyar //
NK038(nyi)001:2201: dgra bgegs mgo lus tshal par gshogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2202: tha ma gnam lcags dbal phur 'debs //
NK038(nyi)001:2203: dmigs pa'i snying la gzer chen 'bebs //
NK038(nyi)001:2204: g.yon gyi dang po dung chen du //
NK038(nyi)001:2205: srid gsum snying khrag blug cing 'thung //
NK038(nyi)001:2206: bar pa rno dbal shun gyi mdung //
NK038(nyi)001:2207: zhing bcu'i snying la gzer chen 'debs //
NK038(nyi)001:2208: tha ma sbrul nag zhags pa yis //
NK038(nyi)001:2210: zhabs bzhi brkyang bskum 'byung po gnon //
NK038(nyi)001:2211: zhing gi g.yang gzhi'i stod g.yogs la //
NK038(nyi)001:2212: gti mug glang chen pags pa gyon //
NK038(nyi)001:2213: zhe sdang stag gi sham thabs la //
NK038(nyi)001:2214: gdug pa sbrul gyi ske rags bcings //
NK038(nyi)001:2215: thod sbrul thal zhag thal bas brgyan //
NK038(nyi)001:2216: gdug rtsub me yi klong na bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)001:2218: sngon gyi dam bca' ma bsnyel bar //
NK038(nyi)001:2219: bcol ba'i las rnams 'grub par mdzod //
NK038(nyi)001:2220: g.yon gyi phyogs nas sku byung ba //
NK038(nyi)001:2221: nye gnas kro d+h+ai sh+w+aa r+ai ma //
NK038(nyi)001:2222: gtum pa'i srin mo 'jigs tshul can //
NK038(nyi)001:2223: zhal gcig phyag gnyis thal ba'i mdog /
NK038(nyi)001:2224: khrag ral dmar po mun ltar gtibs //
NK038(nyi)001:2225: sku stod zhing chen g.yang gzhi la //
NK038(nyi)001:2226: nyi zla gza' skar gzha' tshon 'khrug /
NK038(nyi)001:2227: sku smad stag dang re lde la //
NK038(nyi)001:2228: sbrul nag chu srin thod pas brgyan //
NK038(nyi)001:2229: g.yas pa sbrul zhags yab la 'khyud //
NK038(nyi)001:2230: g.yon pa thod skyogs khrag gis bkang //

NK038(nyi)001:2270: g.yon pa lcags kyus don snying 'byin //
NK038(nyi)001:2271: mi ro rlon pa'i gdan la bzhugs //

NK038(nyi)001:2276: phyag bzhi gdengs pa cho 'phrul lag /

NK038(nyi)001:2282: mi snying za zhing thod rlon 'phen //

NK038(nyi)001:2286: khyod kyi sta zur g.yas g.yon nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2287: pho seng g.yas la mo seng g.yon //
NK038(nyi)001:2288: ral pa sngon po nyigs se nyid //
NK038(nyi)001:2289: mche ba gangs ri gtams pa 'dra //
NK038(nyi)001:2290: khro bo tshogs kyi sprul pa 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)001:2291: khyod kyi rtsib logs g.yon pa nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2292: 'phar ba rkan ldag khyugs se khyug /
NK038(nyi)001:2293: dred mo lag rdebs chems se chem //
NK038(nyi)001:2294: za byed tshogs kyi sprul pa 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)001:2295: khyod kyi smin khyug g.yas g.yon nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2296: bya khyung rgyal po ga ru ta //
NK038(nyi)001:2297: phyag na rdo rje bka' sdod cing //
NK038(nyi)001:2298: srin mo'i tshogs kyi sprul pa 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)001:2299: sho ra re ste ma gtong zhig /
NK038(nyi)001:2300: dur khrod chen pa'i klong dkyil nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2301: srin mo nye gnas chen mo brgyad //
NK038(nyi)001:2302: koo r+ai tsoo r+ai pra mo ha //
NK038(nyi)001:2303: be ta li dang puk+ka s+ai //
NK038(nyi)001:2304: g+hasma r+ai dang sma sha n+ai //
NK038(nyi)001:2305: tsan+da l+ai ste srin mo kun //
NK038(nyi)001:2306: rngam zhing gtum pa'i ma tshogs la //
NK038(nyi)001:2307: 'jigs pa'i gzugs can mtshon cha thogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2308: srog la hur thum dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2309: srin po'i bu mo dri za brgyad //
NK038(nyi)001:2310: seng stag wa spyang bzhad kyi mgo /
NK038(nyi)001:2311: kang ka bya rog 'ug pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2312: zhing la rngam zhing stod pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2313: nyams pa long la glo snying zo //
NK038(nyi)001:2314: cho 'phrul sna tshogs dgra la thong //
NK038(nyi)001:2315: dur khrod ma yi sgo srung bzhi //
NK038(nyi)001:2316: gdong mo brtson mo gar log mo //
NK038(nyi)001:2317: 'jug par byed pa'i ma mo bzhi //
NK038(nyi)001:2319: nyams pa dgra yi yan lag 'chings //
NK038(nyi)001:2320: dur khrod bdag mo gru 'debs bzhi //
NK038(nyi)001:2321: bskam mo shin tu bskam pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2322: ra ro ma dang khrag 'thung ma //
NK038(nyi)001:2323: chags pa'i tshul la bla srog len //
NK038(nyi)001:2324: dam nyams dgra bo'i dbugs long la //
NK038(nyi)001:2325: smyo 'bog gtong ba'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2326: lha yi ded dpon ka ru na //
NK038(nyi)001:2327: chung ma bu mo srin mo rnams //
NK038(nyi)001:2328: phrog nas dbang du byas pa yi //
NK038(nyi)001:2329: bcu gnyis dang ni bco brgyad stsogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2330: ma mo phra men gnod sbyin mo //
NK038(nyi)001:2331: srin mo sha za khrag 'thung ma //
NK038(nyi)001:2332: dam nyams dgra bo'i bkrag mdangs phrogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2333: bdud kyi ming 'dzin bla kun mo //
NK038(nyi)001:2334: dam nyams 'di yi bla long la //
NK038(nyi)001:2335: blon mo dmag dpon sde dpon mo //
NK038(nyi)001:2336: ru dpon pho nya mngag par byas //
NK038(nyi)001:2337: ci bgyis bka' nyan pho nya'i 'khor //
NK038(nyi)001:2338: srin po'i dmag tshogs dgra la thong //
NK038(nyi)001:2339: rbod gtong rngam pas dgra snying khos //
NK038(nyi)001:2340: bam ril thod mkhar phyi rol nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2341: khrag dang sha chen bshang gci dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2342: rkang dang klad pa klad rgyas dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2343: rnag dang chu ser 'obs dang ni //
NK038(nyi)001:2345: sbrang ma sbrang rgod bung ba dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2346: dug sbrul sdig pa sdom la stsogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2347: dgra bo'i khang khyim rmang nas shig /
NK038(nyi)001:2348: dgra bo'i lus la bal ltar g.yengs //
NK038(nyi)001:2349: kang ka ru rtse rkang ldag dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2350: khrag 'thung mchu dmar khwa skyegs dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2351: bya rog 'ug pa khwa rgod rnams //
NK038(nyi)001:2352: bya gcan mang po 'phur zhing lding //
NK038(nyi)001:2353: dgra bo'i bla yi steng du lding //
NK038(nyi)001:2354: sha la za zhing rgyu ma drongs //
NK038(nyi)001:2355: dbang po'i dwangs ma mig 'bras phyung //
NK038(nyi)001:2356: ce spyang stag seng dom dang dred //
NK038(nyi)001:2357: 'phar ba rkang ldag la sogs pa'i //
NK038(nyi)001:2358: gcan gzan gdug pa'i tshogs rnams kun //
NK038(nyi)001:2359: dam nyams sha rus bcud la rol //
NK038(nyi)001:2360: myur du sod la khrag la 'thung //
NK038(nyi)001:2361: dur khrod mkha' 'gro ma mo kun //
NK038(nyi)001:2362: spyugs glu len cing dmag tshogs khye //
NK038(nyi)001:2363: dam nyams srog dbugs mdangs la ya //
NK038(nyi)001:2366: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las //
NK038(nyi)001:2367: dbus kyi gtso bo bskul pa'i le'u ste nyer brgyad pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:2368: de nas 'khor bskul pa 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:2370: shar phyogs thod mkhar 'jigs pa na //
NK038(nyi)001:2371: khro bo'i tshogs dang sprul pa'i 'khor //
NK038(nyi)001:2372: khro chen badz+ra ging ka ra //
NK038(nyi)001:2373: sku mdog mthing nag 'jigs pa'i sku //
NK038(nyi)001:2374: phyag g.yas mtshon cha'i 'khor lo sgyur //
NK038(nyi)001:2375: dmigs pa'i mgo lus dum bur gtubs //
NK038(nyi)001:2376: g.yon pa thod pa rlon pa ru //
NK038(nyi)001:2377: snying khrag 'thungs shing dmigs pa gnon //
NK038(nyi)001:2378: khyod kyi thugs dam dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2379: khyod kyi bka' 'khor las byed ni //

NK038(nyi)001:2381: gsang ba'i bdag pos dbang bskur nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2382: rdo rje chos kyi ming btags pas //
NK038(nyi)001:2384: mthing nag khros pa'i cha byad can //
NK038(nyi)001:2385: ltas ngan sna tshogs sprul pa 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)001:2386: rdo rje myu gu zhes bya ba //
NK038(nyi)001:2387: gri thogs chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2388: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa kun 'dus pas //
NK038(nyi)001:2389: 'od phung khros pa'i khro bo bzhi //
NK038(nyi)001:2390: mi bzad 'bar ba drag po'i gzugs //
NK038(nyi)001:2391: khrag mig dmar po ldog cing khro //
NK038(nyi)001:2392: rdo rje drag po 'khor lo rtsal //
NK038(nyi)001:2393: gri thogs chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2394: dam can khrag gi ral pa can //
NK038(nyi)001:2396: dur khrod mkha' 'gro tshogs kyi bdag /
NK038(nyi)001:2397: rdo rje chos kyi las mkhan po //
NK038(nyi)001:2398: gri thogs chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2399: ser nag 'jig pa'i sbrul gyis brgyan //
NK038(nyi)001:2400: kha nas me 'bar stong gsum bsreg /
NK038(nyi)001:2401: rin chen bdud dpung tshogs kyi bdag /
NK038(nyi)001:2402: rin chen myu gu zhes bya ba //
NK038(nyi)001:2403: gri thogs chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2404: chos bzang lha yi 'dun sa ru //
NK038(nyi)001:2405: lha yi dmag dpon chen po ni //
NK038(nyi)001:2406: ljang nag lus la cho 'phrul can //
NK038(nyi)001:2407: rdo rje las rab drag po rtsal //
NK038(nyi)001:2408: gri thogs ging chen bco brgyad 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)001:2409: nam gyi phar phyed tshur phyed na //
NK038(nyi)001:2410: skyes pa dar ma'i srog gcod cing //
NK038(nyi)001:2411: bud med mngal phug srid kha sdoms //
NK038(nyi)001:2412: spyugs glu len cing 'khor los gcod //
NK038(nyi)001:2413: rdo rje zla rtsal mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)001:2414: gri thogs chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2415: sku mdog dmar gsal khrag gi mdog /
NK038(nyi)001:2416: ce spyang mang po'i sprul pa 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)001:2417: mi bzad lag rings chen po ste //
NK038(nyi)001:2418: rdo rje nyi ma mdangs chen po //
NK038(nyi)001:2419: gri thogs chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2420: rngam pa'i nga ro drag po ni //
NK038(nyi)001:2421: nam mkha'i khams nas 'brug ltar sgrogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2422: mche ba rngam pas dgra snying 'byin //
NK038(nyi)001:2423: rdo rje seng chen mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)001:2424: gri thogs chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2425: nag po mi bzad spyan gsum po //
NK038(nyi)001:2426: shwa na khyi gdong 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK038(nyi)001:2427: lcags kyi spyang mo mgo dgu zhon //
NK038(nyi)001:2428: rdo rje spyang ki mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)001:2429: gri thogs chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2430: mi rtog pa la gnas pa'i sku /
NK038(nyi)001:2431: thogs pa med pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:2432: mtshon cha sna chogs char du 'bebs //
NK038(nyi)001:2433: rdo rje nam mkha' mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)001:2434: gri thogs chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2435: ljang sngon drag po gsal shing can //
NK038(nyi)001:2436: phyogs bzhi dag tu rgyug byed cing //
NK038(nyi)001:2438: rdo rje phyogs 'dul mthu bo che //
NK038(nyi)001:2439: gri thogs chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2440: mthing nag khro bo'i cha byad can //
NK038(nyi)001:2441: mi mgo stong gi phreng bas brgyan //
NK038(nyi)001:2442: mi ro bam pa'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)001:2443: dur khrod bdag po chen po bya //
NK038(nyi)001:2444: gri thogs chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2445: gri thogs ging chen bcu gnyis po //
NK038(nyi)001:2446: la la khrag gi thig le can //
NK038(nyi)001:2447: la la zhag gi zo ris can //
NK038(nyi)001:2448: la la thal chen tshom bu can //
NK038(nyi)001:2449: phyag na lcags gri rnon po brdar //
NK038(nyi)001:2450: glo snying 'byin cing nang khrol za //
NK038(nyi)001:2451: dmigs pa'i dgra la khro tshogs chos //
NK038(nyi)001:2452: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las //
NK038(nyi)001:2453: khro bo'i tshogs bskul ba'i le'u ste nyer dgu pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:2454: de nas gnod sbyin gyi tshogs bskul ba 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:2456: nyi ma nub phyogs pha gi na //
NK038(nyi)001:2457: bse gdong khra mo'i nang shed na //
NK038(nyi)001:2458: lcags mkhar sngon po gnam du ldems se ldem //
NK038(nyi)001:2459: g.yas na pho seng brgya ni kha yang 'thab //
NK038(nyi)001:2460: g.yon na mo seng brgya ni mche ba brdar //
NK038(nyi)001:2461: 'og na zhe sdang dug mtsho'i rba rlabs me re re //
NK038(nyi)001:2462: steng na bse yi bya glag brgyad khri bzhi stong lding //
NK038(nyi)001:2463: sked nas nyi ma zla ba'i 'od zer 'char //
NK038(nyi)001:2464: rtse la nga rgyal glog dmar khyugs se khyug /
NK038(nyi)001:2465: bse 'brug lding ba gnam nas 'khyug cing ldir //
NK038(nyi)001:2466: bse ser lug tsam rtag tu char du 'bebs //
NK038(nyi)001:2467: de 'dra'i mkhar gyi nang shed na //
NK038(nyi)001:2468: ma rungs gdug pa kun gyi gtso gyur pa //
NK038(nyi)001:2469: yab gcig gnod sbyin rgyal po zangs thogs bzhengs //
NK038(nyi)001:2470: sku mdog dmar nag brjid pa la //
NK038(nyi)001:2471: dbu la rgyan mdud 'khor lo brtsegs //
NK038(nyi)001:2472: ral pa dmar po sprin ltar gtibs //
NK038(nyi)001:2473: spyan mig dmar po dam nyams dgra la zlog /
NK038(nyi)001:2474: 'jigs pa'i zhal ni bgrad pa la //
NK038(nyi)001:2475: mche ba gnam lcags dgu brgyas gtams //
NK038(nyi)001:2476: sku la shun gyi g.yang gzhi gsol //
NK038(nyi)001:2477: phyag na gser gyi ral gri bsnams //
NK038(nyi)001:2478: g.yon pa bse yi mdung dmar bsnams //
NK038(nyi)001:2479: ba dan dmar po glog ltar 'khyug /
NK038(nyi)001:2480: 'jigs su rung ba'i dpa' byad can //
NK038(nyi)001:2481: sngon du zhe sdang las la grub //
NK038(nyi)001:2482: do nub drag po'i dus la bab //

NK038(nyi)001:2484: bse gdong zangs mgrin rdzu 'phrul can //
NK038(nyi)001:2485: sngo dmar lus la 'ja' yis brgyan //
NK038(nyi)001:2486: ral pa sngon po bu yug 'tshub //
NK038(nyi)001:2487: g.yas pa byad thag dgra la 'phen //
NK038(nyi)001:2488: g.yon pa sngo dmar bgegs la 'debs //

NK038(nyi)001:2490: 'jigs pa'i spyugs glu tse re re //
NK038(nyi)001:2491: srin po 'bum tshogs dmag tu bskul //
NK038(nyi)001:2492: sngon kyang 'dod chags las las grub //
NK038(nyi)001:2493: do nub drag po'i las la mdzod //
NK038(nyi)001:2494: khyod kyi bka' nyan las byed pa //
NK038(nyi)001:2495: bse yi gyad chen dmag dpon bzhi //
NK038(nyi)001:2496: lha srin sde brgyad las la bskul //
NK038(nyi)001:2497: nyams pa dgra yis gshed ma gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:2498: sa bdag bse yi lha mo bzhi //
NK038(nyi)001:2499: bud med sde bzhis dmag sna drongs //
NK038(nyi)001:2500: 'du ba rnam bzhi nad mtshon rgyob /
NK038(nyi)001:2501: snying zan srog 'dis srog len sogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2502: 'khor gyi ging chen bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK038(nyi)001:2504: stag ral g.yas la gzig shub g.yon //
NK038(nyi)001:2505: phyag na ral gri rno 'joms thogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2506: srog rtsa bcad nas snying khrag 'thung //
NK038(nyi)001:2507: bse phub dmar po me 'od snang srid 'gengs //
NK038(nyi)001:2509: h+aum chen drag po ging gi tshogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2510: sha khrag sna tshogs ging la mchod //
NK038(nyi)001:2511: bcol ba'i las rnams grub par gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:2513: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK038(nyi)001:2514: gnod sbyin gyi tshogs bskul ba'i le'u ste sum bcu pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:2515: de nas rag sha srin po'i tshogs bskul ba 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:2517: drag po lcags mkhar nang shed na //
NK038(nyi)001:2518: rak+sha dz+wa la glog phreng can //
NK038(nyi)001:2519: tam sham bse gdong gdug pa'i bu //
NK038(nyi)001:2520: khyab 'jug chen po kun tu rgyu //
NK038(nyi)001:2521: 'jigs byed chen po kun tu rgyu //
NK038(nyi)001:2522: lus po gcig la mgo bo dgu /
NK038(nyi)001:2523: mgo lus med par mig gis khengs //
NK038(nyi)001:2524: ro stod srin la ro smad sbrul //
NK038(nyi)001:2525: sku mdog brjid pa'i dud kha ba //
NK038(nyi)001:2526: g.yas pa rdo rje gri gug gis //
NK038(nyi)001:2527: nyams pa'i khog gshog snying nas phyung //
NK038(nyi)001:2528: g.yon pa chu srin zhags pa yis /
NK038(nyi)001:2529: bla srog zung zhing dam du chings //
NK038(nyi)001:2530: nyi ma zla ba lto ru za //
NK038(nyi)001:2531: nyi ma'i rjes gcod shar du rgyug /
NK038(nyi)001:2532: zla ba'i rjes gcod nub tu rgyug /
NK038(nyi)001:2533: nyin mo rgyug cing bla srog sdud //
NK038(nyi)001:2534: mtshan mo rgyu zhing srog dbugs gcod //
NK038(nyi)001:2535: dmag dpon chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2536: gza' mchog chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2537: dbang phyug chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2538: nam mkha'i dkyil nas 'brug bsgrags shing //
NK038(nyi)001:2539: bar snang khams nas glog chen 'khyug /
NK038(nyi)001:2540: sa yi dkyil du thog chen 'bebs //
NK038(nyi)001:2541: rgya mtsho'i gting du ser chen sgril //
NK038(nyi)001:2542: dam nyams dgra yi yul 'khor choms //
NK038(nyi)001:2543: lo la khrag gi ser ba phob //
NK038(nyi)001:2544: srog la glo bur ye 'drog thong //
NK038(nyi)001:2545: phyogs bzhi nam mkha'i dkyil yangs nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2546: ngan sngags bdag mo gdong mo bzhi //
NK038(nyi)001:2548: pho lhog nad stsogs nad mtshon rgyob //
NK038(nyi)001:2549: phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi steng 'og nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2550: srid pa'i rgyal po chen po bcu //
NK038(nyi)001:2551: mdog ni ma nges khros pa bzhin //
NK038(nyi)001:2552: mtshon cha sna tshogs 'khor lo sgyur //
NK038(nyi)001:2553: bstan pa bsrung bar dam bcas pa'i //
NK038(nyi)001:2554: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2555: dam nyams srog rtsa dmar po chod //
NK038(nyi)001:2556: ri rab g.yo bsnyil 'u ru ru //
NK038(nyi)001:2557: rgya mtsho zho 'chol chi li li //
NK038(nyi)001:2558: gnam sa dkrug pa'i dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2559: srog rtsa chod cing snying mgo chod //
NK038(nyi)001:2561: dgra bo'i rtsa lag rlung la skur //
NK038(nyi)001:2563: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las //
NK038(nyi)001:2564: srin po'i tshogs las la mngag pa'i le'u ste so gcig pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:2565: de nas za byed ma mo'i tshogs bskul ba 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:2567: nyi ma byang shar pha gi na //
NK038(nyi)001:2568: brag dmar mtsho khol me re re //
NK038(nyi)001:2569: dug rlangs na bun phyu ru ru //
NK038(nyi)001:2570: mtsho chen sngon dmar rba rlabs chi li li //
NK038(nyi)001:2571: bse mkhar smug po gnam du zangs se zang //
NK038(nyi)001:2572: dur bya kang ka sna tshogs lding zhing 'jum //
NK038(nyi)001:2573: ce spyang li ru'i tshogs rnams di ri ri //
NK038(nyi)001:2574: nad kyi mtshon sprin sngon dmar thims se thib //
NK038(nyi)001:2575: ma gcig dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK038(nyi)001:2576: ya mtshan bud med rngam pa'i mdog /
NK038(nyi)001:2577: sku mdog mthing nag 'jigs pa la //
NK038(nyi)001:2578: khrag gi ral pa thun ltar gtibs //
NK038(nyi)001:2579: spyi bo'i gtsug na zla gam gsal //
NK038(nyi)001:2580: lte ba'i dbus nas nyi ma 'char //
NK038(nyi)001:2581: srid gsum kun gsal bla tshe rku //
NK038(nyi)001:2582: snyan cha seng sbrul dril bus brgyan //
NK038(nyi)001:2583: thams cad zil gnon gdug pa 'dul //
NK038(nyi)001:2584: sku stod zhing chen g.yang gzhi la //
NK038(nyi)001:2585: rus phreng khrag dang zhags gis brgyan //
NK038(nyi)001:2586: sku smad re lde'i sham thams la //
NK038(nyi)001:2587: sbrul dang thod phreng dril bus brgyan //
NK038(nyi)001:2588: chibs su dre'u rta rkang gsum chibs //
NK038(nyi)001:2589: drag mo mtshon cha'i lte le can //
NK038(nyi)001:2590: g.yas na gshin rje'i khram bam bsnams //
NK038(nyi)001:2591: g.yon na nad kyi rkyal pa bsnams //
NK038(nyi)001:2592: btsan gyi shwa rdel phyogs bcur 'thor //
NK038(nyi)001:2593: tshub nag stong dkyil nang na bzhugs //
NK038(nyi)001:2594: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2595: shar phyogs khams kyi za byed ma //
NK038(nyi)001:2596: sangs rgyas rigs kyi rnal 'byor ma //
NK038(nyi)001:2597: dkar mo ral can 'bum sde rnams //
NK038(nyi)001:2598: khyod kyis shar phyogs dgra bgegs thul //
NK038(nyi)001:2599: lho phyogs rigs kyi za byed ma //
NK038(nyi)001:2600: ser mo ral can khros pa'i gdong //
NK038(nyi)001:2601: rin chen rigs kyi rnal 'byor ma //
NK038(nyi)001:2602: khyod kyis lho yi dgra bgegs thul //
NK038(nyi)001:2603: nub phyogs khams kyi za byed ma //
NK038(nyi)001:2604: dmar mo ral can pho nyar bcas //
NK038(nyi)001:2606: khyod kyis nub kyi dgra bgegs thul //
NK038(nyi)001:2607: byang gi phyogs gyi za byed ma //
NK038(nyi)001:2608: ljang nag ral can rngam pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2609: las kyi rigs kyi rnal 'byor ma //
NK038(nyi)001:2610: khyod kyis byang gi dgra bgegs thul //
NK038(nyi)001:2612: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las //
NK038(nyi)001:2613: ma mo'i tshogs bskul ba'i le'u ste so gnyis pa'o //
NK038(nyi)001:2614: de nas drag po gshin rje ltar bskul ba 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:2616: dur khrod chen po'i gnas mchog nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2618: thod mkhar sgo med nang shed na //
NK038(nyi)001:2619: mi ro rta ro gcal du bkram //
NK038(nyi)001:2620: gzas pa'i gdan la stag chen khri //
NK038(nyi)001:2621: me dpung klong nas sku byung ba //
NK038(nyi)001:2622: ma h+aa k+aa la mgon po che /
NK038(nyi)001:2625: spyan gsum ldang mig me ltar 'bar //
NK038(nyi)001:2626: dgra bo'i dus srog dbang po 'byin //
NK038(nyi)001:2627: shar nas rims dal rlung dmar g.yo //
NK038(nyi)001:2628: stong khams thams cad nad kyis khengs //
NK038(nyi)001:2629: zhal gdangs rno dbal mche ba gtsigs //
NK038(nyi)001:2630: dmigs pa'i dgra bo ril mig byed /
NK038(nyi)001:2631: rngam pa'i ra ro 'brug stong sgrogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2632: bdud dang mu stegs brgyal bar byed //
NK038(nyi)001:2633: sku la ber nag brtsegs pa gsol //
NK038(nyi)001:2634: dpa' brtul stag gi slog pa la //
NK038(nyi)001:2636: dpa' brtul dur khrod chas kyis brgyan //
NK038(nyi)001:2637: g.yas pa tsan dan bing chen gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:2638: dam nyams dgra bo rdul du rlogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2639: phyag g.yon thod khrag dmar chen 'thung //
NK038(nyi)001:2640: drag po rdzu 'phrul bsam mi khyab //
NK038(nyi)001:2641: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2642: de yi yum chen srin mo'i sku //
NK038(nyi)001:2643: mthing nag brjid pa'i tshul gyis 'khril //
NK038(nyi)001:2644: sbrul nag ral ba mun ltar gtibs //
NK038(nyi)001:2645: dur khrod na bza' sku la gsol //
NK038(nyi)001:2646: g.yas pa rgyu zhags bla srog 'gugs //
NK038(nyi)001:2647: g.yon pa thod khrag dal yams 'bebs //
NK038(nyi)001:2648: mon pa nag po'i tshogs kyis bskor //
NK038(nyi)001:2650: khyod kyi dgra bgegs myur du sgrol //
NK038(nyi)001:2651: bdud yul kha rag mgo dgu ma //
NK038(nyi)001:2652: bdud nag ri nag spungs pa yang //
NK038(nyi)001:2653: bdud mkhar nang nas 'dir byon la //
NK038(nyi)001:2654: dgra la thibs nad thong la sgrol //
NK038(nyi)001:2655: rgya yul nam mkha'i phyar phyod nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2656: srog bdag 'od lha dkar po yang //
NK038(nyi)001:2657: shel mkhar nang nas 'dir byon la //
NK038(nyi)001:2658: dgra la smyo 'bog thong la sgrol //
NK038(nyi)001:2659: mang yul byang shar mtsho gling nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2660: ma mo rdo rje sder mo yang //
NK038(nyi)001:2661: mthing nag gur nas las la chos //
NK038(nyi)001:2662: dgra la dal yams thong la sgrol //
NK038(nyi)001:2663: klu yul na ra sing chen nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2664: klu gnyan nag po srog len yang //
NK038(nyi)001:2665: rin chen mkhar nas sku bskyod la //
NK038(nyi)001:2666: dgra la mdze shu phol 'bras thong //
NK038(nyi)001:2667: btsan yul zangs thang dmar po nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2668: btsan rje shu po lag ring kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:2669: bse mkhar nang nas sku bskyod la //
NK038(nyi)001:2670: dgra la gri thabs thong la sgrol //
NK038(nyi)001:2671: shar phyogs rin chen gling thang nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2672: ging gi rdo rje legs pa yang //
NK038(nyi)001:2673: lung thang mkhar nas 'dir byon la //
NK038(nyi)001:2674: dgra la pho lhog hur thum thong //
NK038(nyi)001:2676: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las //
NK038(nyi)001:2677: sgrol ging chen po las la bskul ba'i le'u ste so gsum pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:2678: de nas dpa' bo ging chen gyi bskul pa 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:2680: dur khrod thod pa'i sku mkhar nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2681: gsang bdag thugs kyi sprul pa ni //
NK038(nyi)001:2682: gsod byed ging chen las la bskul //
NK038(nyi)001:2683: sku mdog dmar po khros pa la //
NK038(nyi)001:2684: gdug pa'i me 'od lams se lam /
NK038(nyi)001:2685: dbu la bse rtog dmar po gsol //
NK038(nyi)001:2687: le brgan dar gyi cod pan la /
NK038(nyi)001:2689: spyan mig dmar po bzlog pa yis //
NK038(nyi)001:2690: bdud dang mu stegs zil gyis gnon //
NK038(nyi)001:2691: khros pa'i gad mo rkan brdabs pas //
NK038(nyi)001:2692: ma tshogs srin po 'dar spyug spyug /
NK038(nyi)001:2693: gsang ba'i spyugs pa tse re re //
NK038(nyi)001:2694: sgrol ging dmar po las la 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)001:2695: phyag g.yas zangs gri rno dbal gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:2696: nyams pa dgra bo'i srog lus 'brol //
NK038(nyi)001:2697: g.yon pas tsit+ta phyung nas gsol //
NK038(nyi)001:2698: ye shes ging gi 'khor gyis bskor //
NK038(nyi)001:2699: sprul pa'i ging tshogs stong gsum sreg /
NK038(nyi)001:2700: las kyi ging phran las la 'gyed //
NK038(nyi)001:2701: dpa' bo ging chen las la chos //
NK038(nyi)001:2702: shar phyogs srin po'i yul rtse nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2703: pra ma r+aa dza srin po'i gtso //
NK038(nyi)001:2705: shel gyi zangs gris dgra la 'debs //
NK038(nyi)001:2706: tsit+ta phyung nas zhal du gsol //
NK038(nyi)001:2707: srin po'i 'khor tshogs las la chos //
NK038(nyi)001:2708: lho phyogs gshin rje'i yul rtse nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2709: ya ma r+aa dza gshin rje'i gtso //
NK038(nyi)001:2710: sku mdog nag po mun rum 'dra //
NK038(nyi)001:2711: lcags kyi zangs gri dgra la 'debs //
NK038(nyi)001:2712: tsit+ta phyung nas zhal du gsol //
NK038(nyi)001:2713: gshin rje'i dmag tshogs dgra la chos //
NK038(nyi)001:2714: nub phyogs srin po'i yul rtse nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2715: ha nu dpag shu bdud gyi gtso //
NK038(nyi)001:2717: zangs kyi ral gri dgra la 'debs //
NK038(nyi)001:2718: tsit+ta phyung nas zhal du gsol //
NK038(nyi)001:2719: bdud kyi 'khor tshogs dgra la ya //
NK038(nyi)001:2720: byang phyogs gnod sbyin yul rtse nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2721: yag sha gar ba gnod sbyin gtso //
NK038(nyi)001:2723: gser gyi ral gri dgra la 'debs //
NK038(nyi)001:2724: tsit+ta phyung nas zhal du gsol //
NK038(nyi)001:2725: gnod sbyin 'khor tshogs las la chos //
NK038(nyi)001:2727: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las //
NK038(nyi)001:2728: ging chen las la bskul ba'i le'u ste so bzhi pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:2729: de nas rgyud gtan tshigs kyi le'u 'di bshad do //
NK038(nyi)001:2730: 'das ba'i dus na sngon byung ba'i //
NK038(nyi)001:2731: bskal pa rjogs ldan bya ba la //
NK038(nyi)001:2732: mi bskyod zhing khams mngon dga' ba'i //
NK038(nyi)001:2733: lho phyogs 'dzam bu'i gling de ru //
NK038(nyi)001:2734: khyim bdag ko'u ka ya zhes //
NK038(nyi)001:2735: bya ba de la bu gcig yod //
NK038(nyi)001:2736: de ming thar pa nag po bya //
NK038(nyi)001:2737: kho bo dang pa'i sems g.yos te //
NK038(nyi)001:2738: yul phyogs de yi dgon pa na //
NK038(nyi)001:2739: dge slong thub dka' gzhon zhu zhes //
NK038(nyi)001:2740: bya ba gsang sngags don rtogs pa //
NK038(nyi)001:2741: yon tan kho na de thos te //
NK038(nyi)001:2742: dan phag g.yog dang bcas pa yis //
NK038(nyi)001:2743: de drung phyin te gdam pa zhus //
NK038(nyi)001:2744: de nyid kyis kyang gdams pa gnang //
NK038(nyi)001:2745: ji bzhin nyid de ma bcos na //
NK038(nyi)001:2746: dngos po bzhi la spyad byas kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:2747: nam mkha' la ni sprin bzhin te //
NK038(nyi)001:2748: de ni rnal 'byor dam pa'i lam //
NK038(nyi)001:2749: de skad gdams pa phog pa las //
NK038(nyi)001:2750: kho bdag dga' mgu gnas su dengs //
NK038(nyi)001:2751: don gyi bden thob ma rnyed par //
NK038(nyi)001:2752: sgra bzhin 'dod yon lnga la zhen //
NK038(nyi)001:2753: nam zhig dpon g.yog ma mthun te //
NK038(nyi)001:2754: rtsod gyur dge slong dpon la dris //
NK038(nyi)001:2755: thub dkas rang bzhin so so nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2756: dan phag bden no zhes gsungs pas //
NK038(nyi)001:2757: thar pa nag po khams 'khrugs te //
NK038(nyi)001:2758: gnyis ka'i dpon du 'dra ba la //
NK038(nyi)001:2759: mnyam mo zhes kyang mi brjod par //
NK038(nyi)001:2760: nges par rang nyid sun phyung bas //
NK038(nyi)001:2761: khams 'dir ma chags bya snyam ste //
NK038(nyi)001:2762: de nas dpon g.yog gnyis spyug btang //
NK038(nyi)001:2763: gsang sngags rdo rje'i bka' bsgo log /
NK038(nyi)001:2765: lta ba thams cad log par 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:2766: thams cad log pa'i rgya mtshor zhugs //
NK038(nyi)001:2767: log pa'i dka' thub drag po dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2768: log pa'i brtul zhugs chen po yis //
NK038(nyi)001:2769: sha rlon za zhing lpags rlon gyon //
NK038(nyi)001:2770: sha za'i zag pa mang bsogs te //
NK038(nyi)001:2771: thams cad bsad cing sha rlon zos //
NK038(nyi)001:2772: rigs byed sngags kyi brda' spros te //
NK038(nyi)001:2773: mo rigs phrad pa thams cad sbyor //
NK038(nyi)001:2775: gnas pa'i dus med tshe zad nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2776: skye ba lnga brgya ce spyang lus su skyes //
NK038(nyi)001:2777: gnyen pos bsad cing tshe 'phos gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:2778: ngan skyugs phyi yi srin bu dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2779: mi gtsang nang gi srin bur skyes //
NK038(nyi)001:2780: gnyen pos bsad cing tshe 'phos gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:2781: ro dang stong phrag re lde yi //
NK038(nyi)001:2782: nang rtsa gnas pa'i srog chags gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:2783: de mthar mngal gyi srin bur skyes //
NK038(nyi)001:2784: na rag rdo rje dmyal bar gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:2785: tshe tshad tshe lo brgyad khrir gnas //
NK038(nyi)001:2786: thub pa chos kyi rgyal po yis //
NK038(nyi)001:2787: las su bstan pas der shes te //
NK038(nyi)001:2788: 'gyod pas rim bzhin tsha dmyal brgyad //
NK038(nyi)001:2789: rim bzhin gong nas gong du 'phos //
NK038(nyi)001:2790: bde ba bral zhing phun ring 'khor //
NK038(nyi)001:2791: de nas bsad cing thon thar nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2792: nad mtshon mu ge'i bskal pa brgyud //
NK038(nyi)001:2793: gzhan gyi longs spyod phyir bsad de //
NK038(nyi)001:2795: sha za ma dang srul por skyes //
NK038(nyi)001:2796: de ltar skye ba rgyud pa'i mthar //
NK038(nyi)001:2797: lho nub lang ka pu ri yi //
NK038(nyi)001:2798: smad 'tshong ma yi mngal du chags //
NK038(nyi)001:2799: bu de thon pas ma de 'chi //
NK038(nyi)001:2800: yul phyogs de yi mi dag gis //
NK038(nyi)001:2801: pha med do bu ko nu 'di //
NK038(nyi)001:2802: bzhag na yul phyogs sme bas na //
NK038(nyi)001:2803: ma yi ro mchan gzhug par bsgos //
NK038(nyi)001:2804: dug shing nal bya'i rtsa ru bskyal //
NK038(nyi)001:2805: bu des mi yi nu ma drangs //
NK038(nyi)001:2806: de nas khrag dang chu ser drangs //
NK038(nyi)001:2807: de nas ma ro zad par zos //
NK038(nyi)001:2808: rang brgyud khro bo'i 'jigs par bsgom //
NK038(nyi)001:2809: ma yi pags pa gos su gyon /
NK038(nyi)001:2810: de nas pa tra lus chen brtas //
NK038(nyi)001:2811: dur khrod ro yi sha khrag zos //
NK038(nyi)001:2812: thod phreng sor phreng rgyan du byas //
NK038(nyi)001:2813: ro yi pags pa gos su gyon //
NK038(nyi)001:2814: dur khrod nas pa'i mkha' 'gro rnams //
NK038(nyi)001:2815: chung ma slas dang bran du byas //
NK038(nyi)001:2816: ma zan r+au tra de yi ni //
NK038(nyi)001:2817: kha nas tsha ba'i dbugs byung nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2818: nad dang rims kyis thams cad gsod //
NK038(nyi)001:2819: sna nas grang ba'i dbugs byung bas //
NK038(nyi)001:2820: phyogs bcu kun tu mas 'khrug byed //
NK038(nyi)001:2821: mig gi dug gis thams cad gsod //
NK038(nyi)001:2822: sngags kyi zer mas thams cad sgrol //
NK038(nyi)001:2823: rang lus thal kha 'jigs pa la //
NK038(nyi)001:2824: mgo gsum lag drug gshog pa can //
NK038(nyi)001:2825: mig gsum skra ni me ltar 'bar //
NK038(nyi)001:2826: gnam la bya bzhin sa la byi //
NK038(nyi)001:2827: chu la nya bzhin 'phyo bar byed //
NK038(nyi)001:2828: sen mo kang ka'i mchu sder gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:2829: gang zin sha rus myags par byed //
NK038(nyi)001:2830: rang gi nga rgyal gtum skad sgrogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2831: de tsho 'gro ba thams cad kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:2832: log lta sna dgu'i lam la btsud //
NK038(nyi)001:2833: nga rgyal che ba'i mthus snyems pas //
NK038(nyi)001:2834: lang ka'i yul gyi grong rdal bcom //
NK038(nyi)001:2835: ko ka thang dmar mtsho yi do //
NK038(nyi)001:2836: byan lag mchong ri ma la ya //
NK038(nyi)001:2837: gnam lcags yod pa'i rtse mo ru //
NK038(nyi)001:2838: srin po'i rgyal po dbang du bsdus //
NK038(nyi)001:2839: ru tra ma tra m+aa r+aa tra //
NK038(nyi)001:2840: rang gi gtum skad drag tu bsgrags //
NK038(nyi)001:2841: srin po'i rgyal po chen po des //
NK038(nyi)001:2842: mngon shes gsang sngags 'byung bar mthong //
NK038(nyi)001:2843: kun kyang 'khor dang g.yog rje byas //
NK038(nyi)001:2844: ded dpon ma ham ka ru tra //
NK038(nyi)001:2845: rang gi nga rgyal che ba rtsol //
NK038(nyi)001:2846: lha yi ded dpon ka ru na /
NK038(nyi)001:2847: ngan thabs tsha ba'i dbugs kyis bsad //
NK038(nyi)001:2848: ro de 'dzam bu'i gling du bor //
NK038(nyi)001:2849: dge gnas mchod rten brgyad du snang //
NK038(nyi)001:2850: 'khor rnams g.yog bzhi gtso mo dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2851: byin dang bran slas pho nya 'khor //
NK038(nyi)001:2852: g.yo 'gul thams cad dbang du byas //
NK038(nyi)001:2853: bam ril thod pa'i mkhar brtsigs nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2854: bdud kyi rgyal mtshan phyogs su btsugs //
NK038(nyi)001:2855: bdud kyi ru mtshon rtse la 'phyar //
NK038(nyi)001:2856: 'dam gyi phru bas yongs su bskor //
NK038(nyi)001:2857: rdzu 'phrul ston cing h+aum skad sgrogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2859: sngon gyi gtsang ma 'phags pas kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:2860: bdag la bka' nyon zer ba la //
NK038(nyi)001:2861: mi nyan slar la gnas su log /
NK038(nyi)001:2862: ngag gi dbang phyug de bzhin byas //
NK038(nyi)001:2863: 'gran zla med ces de bzhin sgrogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2864: ru tra nag po smin par gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:2865: de nas de yi dus nyid na //
NK038(nyi)001:2866: thub dka' rdo rje snying por smin //
NK038(nyi)001:2867: dan phag rtsal chen rdzogs par gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:2868: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kun //
NK038(nyi)001:2869: snying po byang chub nyid du 'dus //
NK038(nyi)001:2870: stong nyid ngang du stong pa'i sgra //
NK038(nyi)001:2871: sangs rgyas mdzad pa ma rdzogs par //
NK038(nyi)001:2872: mngon par sangs rgyas ci phyir yin //
NK038(nyi)001:2873: de bzhin nyid dang kun snang dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2874: yi ge'i rang bzhin skul bar mdzad //
NK038(nyi)001:2875: stong nyid me long mi rtogs las //
NK038(nyi)001:2876: ma skyes mi snang 'gag gzugs snang //
NK038(nyi)001:2877: mkha' la snang mdzad ji bzhin du //
NK038(nyi)001:2878: dbyings las phyag rgya'i sku snang bzhengs //
NK038(nyi)001:2879: go 'byed phyag rgyas kun bsdus nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2880: bde gshegs dgongs pa mthun par grol //
NK038(nyi)001:2881: rnam bzhi'i las kyis bskos btab nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2882: bcom ldan sh+aaka thub can du gshegs //
NK038(nyi)001:2883: rgyu 'bras las kyi dge sdig brjod //
NK038(nyi)001:2884: brtul bas ma thul kho na re //
NK038(nyi)001:2885: mi thub pa yi ngag smras te //
NK038(nyi)001:2886: bu chung rang gi gnas su dengs //
NK038(nyi)001:2887: sngon khyod lta bus nga ma thul //
NK038(nyi)001:2888: de bas rang gi bka' thub gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:2889: zer bas gtsang rigs slar log go //
NK038(nyi)001:2890: de nas sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:2891: rta mgrin dbang bskur thad du gshegs //
NK038(nyi)001:2892: rdo rje rta thabs kho na yis //
NK038(nyi)001:2893: kho rang nyid kyi gtam sgra bsgrags //
NK038(nyi)001:2894: mgrin bu rang gi zas zo dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2895: des ni rta mchog slar la gshegs //
NK038(nyi)001:2896: kha nas khong du rta mchog mid //
NK038(nyi)001:2897: dpal gyis bzhengs te h+aum sgra bsgrags //
NK038(nyi)001:2898: kho yis skad ngan gdung pa bton //
NK038(nyi)001:2899: gnyen po rdo rje h+aum bsgoms pas //
NK038(nyi)001:2900: de la skyabs nyid tshol cig gsungs //
NK038(nyi)001:2901: rta mchog spyi gtsug 'thon te gshegs //
NK038(nyi)001:2902: de nas 'dus pa chen po kun //
NK038(nyi)001:2903: dbang drag gnyis kyis 'dul bar dgongs //
NK038(nyi)001:2904: de dag thams cad kun 'dus nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2905: dur khrod gar gyi phyag rgyar bzhengs //
NK038(nyi)001:2906: khyod kyi rgyu rkyen 'bras bu dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2907: skyon dang yon tan kun dris pas //
NK038(nyi)001:2908: sangs rgyas kun gyis 'di skad gsungs //
NK038(nyi)001:2909: rgyu ni smug po'i ro las byung //
NK038(nyi)001:2910: rkyen ni log pa'i dka' thub gyis //
NK038(nyi)001:2911: 'bras bu sdug bsngal ngo bor smin //
NK038(nyi)001:2912: rigs ni dman rigs 'khor ba'i rigs //
NK038(nyi)001:2913: ngo bo yi dwags srin po de //
NK038(nyi)001:2915: bdud rnams btul na bstan pa dar //
NK038(nyi)001:2916: las ngan 'phro bcad dmyal yun thung //
NK038(nyi)001:2917: thugs rjes bzung na bsod nams tshang //
NK038(nyi)001:2918: stong gsum ma lus bton pa bas //
NK038(nyi)001:2919: 'bum gyi char yang mi phod gsungs //
NK038(nyi)001:2920: de nas sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:2921: nga la thul cig pa ru bskul //
NK038(nyi)001:2922: khams gsum rdo rje bya sgron mngag /
NK038(nyi)001:2923: dbang gi khro bos bar snang dgang //
NK038(nyi)001:2924: bam ril thod pa mkhar gyi phyi //
NK038(nyi)001:2925: bshul bshad 'obs chen byed pa'i brgyad kyis bskor //
NK038(nyi)001:2926: sngon du bshad pa'i 'khor tshogs dang //
NK038(nyi)001:2927: kho bdag lings la yongs nas ni //
NK038(nyi)001:2928: 'khor ni phal cher las la gram //
NK038(nyi)001:2929: skabs su dngos min sprul pa'i sras //
NK038(nyi)001:2930: rdo rje gzhon nu sme ba brtsegs //
NK038(nyi)001:2931: mthing nag 'jigs pa'i khro bo ni //
NK038(nyi)001:2932: blang dor med pa'i mdzad spyod kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:2933: bshang ba thams cad bdud rtsir bsgyur //
NK038(nyi)001:2934: thams cad stong nyid bdud rtsi sbyangs //
NK038(nyi)001:2935: nye gnas bu mo la sogs pa //
NK038(nyi)001:2936: ma chags thabs kyi sbyor ba yis //
NK038(nyi)001:2937: rigs dang mthun pa'i sras de mthong //
NK038(nyi)001:2938: de bzhag gzhan rnams ring du spras //
NK038(nyi)001:2939: ye shes sprul pa'i 'khor du ldan //
NK038(nyi)001:2940: 'dod pa'i dbang mo bskams ma la //
NK038(nyi)001:2941: 'dod pas zhe sdang the tshom skyes //
NK038(nyi)001:2942: dpal gyis srin skad gsungs bsgrags pas //
NK038(nyi)001:2943: the tshom chod de sku la 'khril //
NK038(nyi)001:2944: 'jig rten dregs pa'i srog sngags de //
NK038(nyi)001:2945: ye shes lha yi snying por brlabs //
NK038(nyi)001:2946: lhums su rdo rje srin po bzhag /
NK038(nyi)001:2947: dpal chen gshegs nas kho 'doms pas //
NK038(nyi)001:2949: bdag gi dbang mo 'khor rnams kun //
NK038(nyi)001:2950: sngon dang mi 'dra nges snyam pas //
NK038(nyi)001:2951: chags pa'i dbang mos 'di skad brjod //
NK038(nyi)001:2952: e ma dpa' bo sgeg po khyod //
NK038(nyi)001:2953: bdag gi mngal ni mi bde bas //
NK038(nyi)001:2954: khyod kyi dngos po phyin pa las //
NK038(nyi)001:2956: brjod pas mdangs la chags gyur te //
NK038(nyi)001:2957: dga' ba'i thabs kyis gnyis med 'khril //
NK038(nyi)001:2958: de nas pu tra 'thon byung nas //
NK038(nyi)001:2959: kho rang lta bu'i rigs su byung //
NK038(nyi)001:2960: nag po dpon g.yog yi rang dga' //
NK038(nyi)001:2961: myur bar pu tra lus bltam ste //
NK038(nyi)001:2962: srin skad thang gsum bsgrags pa las //
NK038(nyi)001:2963: dpal gyi rngam sgra drag po des //
NK038(nyi)001:2964: drag po drag mo 'khor tshogs brgyal //
NK038(nyi)001:2965: sangs nas bltas pas cha lugs 'gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:2966: sngo nag dbu dgu bco brgyad phyag /
NK038(nyi)001:2967: sngon du brjod pa nyid du gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:2968: nag po'i stobs dang dbang thang phrogs //
NK038(nyi)001:2969: de nas rlu tra nag po des //
NK038(nyi)001:2970: rang gi nga rgyal h+aum skad kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:2971: rang gi bdud kyi dmag tshogs bsdus //
NK038(nyi)001:2973: mdza' bshes rtag par ma byung na //
NK038(nyi)001:2974: skyid pa'i grogs kyi mi phan pas //
NK038(nyi)001:2975: gang 'dir las rnams dus la bab //
NK038(nyi)001:2976: brjod bas bdud dmag bye ba 'dus //
NK038(nyi)001:2977: mtshon cha'i dbal ni sprin ltar gtibs //
NK038(nyi)001:2978: bso dang cho yi sgra bsgrags te //
NK038(nyi)001:2979: ma la ya yi rtse la chas //
NK038(nyi)001:2980: de nas rdo rje rta gdong gis //
NK038(nyi)001:2981: rdo rje mgros bu'i stangs stabs mdzad //
NK038(nyi)001:2982: gar dgu'i 'bar ba'i glu blangs pas //
NK038(nyi)001:2983: khyo pho sgrol la chung ma drongs //
NK038(nyi)001:2984: phyogs ris med pa'i snying rjes bskul //
NK038(nyi)001:2985: rdo rje rta gdong gzi brjid kyis //
NK038(nyi)001:2986: bdud dmag thams cad zil gyis gnon //
NK038(nyi)001:2987: ru mtshon sprin phung stong nyid sangs //
NK038(nyi)001:2988: mi snyan sgra rnams sngags sgrar bsgyur //
NK038(nyi)001:2989: bdud kyi 'khor tshogs thams cad kun //
NK038(nyi)001:2990: rta mgrin dam la skyabs su dong //
NK038(nyi)001:2991: de nas r+au tra thabs zad de //
NK038(nyi)001:2992: rang gi rdzu 'phrul sngags lnga yis //
NK038(nyi)001:2993: r+au tra lnga yi mthu bskyed kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:2994: dpal gyi de bas mthu che bas //
NK038(nyi)001:2995: mthu stobs med par brgyal bar gyur //
NK038(nyi)001:2996: dpal gyi thugs rje'i gsung du brjod //
NK038(nyi)001:2997: srog gi dbang po mi bzod kyang //
NK038(nyi)001:2999: gang der mdun gyi phyogs nas bsgral //
NK038(nyi)001:3000: rtse gsum 'bar ba'i phyag rgya bcas //
NK038(nyi)001:3001: r+au tra'i ri bo bcom dbang gis //
NK038(nyi)001:3002: phyag rgyas rol te phyag du sbyangs //
NK038(nyi)001:3003: thugs dam dbang gis mtshams sbyar te //
NK038(nyi)001:3004: rang gi dam pa rnam gnyis dang //
NK038(nyi)001:3005: mthar thug med pa'i sangs rgyas dang //
NK038(nyi)001:3006: dpag du med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK038(nyi)001:3007: sdug po bkod pa mthong ba'i sa //
NK038(nyi)001:3008: thog ma med pa'i dus mtha' yi //
NK038(nyi)001:3009: zhen pa'i mun pa sangs gyur te /
NK038(nyi)001:3010: skye ba dus mtha' med rnyed nas //
NK038(nyi)001:3011: lus blangs nas ni ci spyad dran //
NK038(nyi)001:3012: snam du bton nas zhabs drung 'khod //
NK038(nyi)001:3013: rab tu dga' yang nongs tshul du //
NK038(nyi)001:3014: gang der shin tu gdung zhing rmongs //
NK038(nyi)001:3016: kun la rang tshig gsang du byin //
NK038(nyi)001:3017: mnas por nas ni skabs su yang //
NK038(nyi)001:3018: gsang ba'i srog snying byin gyis brlabs //
NK038(nyi)001:3019: rang stobs 'gyod pa drag po dang //
NK038(nyi)001:3020: gzhan gyi ston pas spyo bas sbyong //
NK038(nyi)001:3021: rdo rje theg pa'i gsang sgor bzhag /
NK038(nyi)001:3022: 'khor rnams kun la'ang de bzhin te //
NK038(nyi)001:3023: dbang bskur gsang ba'i ming rnams brtags //
NK038(nyi)001:3024: bskal bzang bstan pa rdzogs pa ru //
NK038(nyi)001:3025: dgongs pa mya ngan 'das kyi bar //
NK038(nyi)001:3026: 'jig rten tshul gyis bstan pa srung //
NK038(nyi)001:3028: zhing khams thal bas khengs pa ru //
NK038(nyi)001:3029: thal ba'i dbang po dbyangs zhes byar //
NK038(nyi)001:3031: de phyir dpal mgon nag po yi //
NK038(nyi)001:3032: rabs rgyud gtan tshigs rgyas par bshad //
NK038(nyi)001:3034: dpal mgon po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las //
NK038(nyi)001:3035: rabs rgyud gtan tshigs kyi le'u ste so lnga pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:3036: de nas 'khor la rgyud gtad pa 'di gsungs so //
NK038(nyi)001:3037: e ma ho 'khor du 'dus pa'i tshogs //
NK038(nyi)001:3038: chos sku rnam dag brjod med pas //
NK038(nyi)001:3039: gdul dka' drag po 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK038(nyi)001:3040: bder gsheg longs spyod rdzogs skur bzhengs //
NK038(nyi)001:3041: sprul pa gang la gang 'dul ston //
NK038(nyi)001:3042: gsang sngags thugs rje rol par shar //
NK038(nyi)001:3043: rtags dang thugs rje sbyin bdag dpal //
NK038(nyi)001:3044: de yi phrin las 'gro ba'i mgon //
NK038(nyi)001:3045: gnas lugs rtogs pas 'gyur ba med //
NK038(nyi)001:3046: chos nyid ngang du mtshan ma yi //
NK038(nyi)001:3047: rnam rtog bsdus bcom dur khrod yin //
NK038(nyi)001:3048: gnas lugs mngon par rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK038(nyi)001:3049: ye shes rol pa cir yang 'chang //
NK038(nyi)001:3050: zhen snang rtog pa'i bag chags dang //
NK038(nyi)001:3051: zhing bcu gcod pa'i mtshon cha yin //
NK038(nyi)001:3052: 'khor lo rnam pa gsum yin te //
NK038(nyi)001:3053: gnas pa rtsa yi tsakra dang //
NK038(nyi)001:3056: dang po bde chen longs spyod dang //
NK038(nyi)001:3057: chos dang sprul pa skye gnas lnga //
NK038(nyi)001:3059: sems kyis de rtog de nyid grol //
NK038(nyi)001:3061: nam zla dus bzhi lo zla zhag /
NK038(nyi)001:3062: 'jig dang stong dang chags pa rnams //
NK038(nyi)001:3063: skye rga na 'chi bzhi ldan pas //
NK038(nyi)001:3064: mgal me lta bur 'khor zhing gnas //
NK038(nyi)001:3065: shing rta'am zo chu lta bu'o //
NK038(nyi)001:3066: las grub 'khor lo gsum yin te //
NK038(nyi)001:3067: bsnyen pa gnas 'gyur lha yi 'khor lo dang //
NK038(nyi)001:3068: sgrub pa gnas 'gyur sngags kyi 'khor lo dang /
NK038(nyi)001:3069: sbyor ba rten 'brel rdzas kyi 'khor lo'o //
NK038(nyi)001:3070: dang po lhar gsal rtsa ba'i drod thob cing //
NK038(nyi)001:3071: de bzhin nyid dang phyag rgya dang //
NK038(nyi)001:3072: byang chub sems dang tshogs rnams so //
NK038(nyi)001:3073: sngags kyi rtsa ba yan lag ni //
NK038(nyi)001:3074: bsnyen bsgrub rtsa ba'i las sngags so //
NK038(nyi)001:3075: bka' sdod las dang gnan pa yi //
NK038(nyi)001:3076: bsnyen mchod bskang dang dmu thun dang //
NK038(nyi)001:3077: dmigs pa rten gyi rdzas rnams te //
NK038(nyi)001:3078: rang rang rten 'brel mthu yis klus //
NK038(nyi)001:3079: de ltar rnams pa kun tshogs pas //
NK038(nyi)001:3080: las rnams thams cad grub pa ni //
NK038(nyi)001:3081: sha ma ta yi 'jig rten na //
NK038(nyi)001:3082: mtshon cha'i 'khor lo lta bu ste /
NK038(nyi)001:3084: rgyud ces bya bar gang gsungs pa //
NK038(nyi)001:3085: rgyud dang thabs dang 'bras bu dang //
NK038(nyi)001:3086: lta spyod dkyil 'khor dbang dam dang //
NK038(nyi)001:3087: sgrub dang phyag rgya zin pas sngags /
NK038(nyi)001:3088: de mtshan pas na rgyun mi 'chad //
NK038(nyi)001:3089: bde bar gshegs pa'i dgongs pa dang //
NK038(nyi)001:3091: yid bzhin nor bu lta bu 'di //
NK038(nyi)001:3092: sbyor ba du ma rtsa ba'i gnad //
NK038(nyi)001:3093: byang chub sems dang khro tshogs dang //
NK038(nyi)001:3095: gshin rje bdud dang dmu btsan rgyal po dang //
NK038(nyi)001:3096: srin po dang ni lha mo dang //
NK038(nyi)001:3098: gnyan dang sa bdag 'khor srun gza' //
NK038(nyi)001:3099: ging dang byad stems dregs pa'i 'khor //
NK038(nyi)001:3100: gsang ba'i bka' rgyud rol pa las //
NK038(nyi)001:3101: sgrub dang 'chang dang gnyer ba dang //
NK038(nyi)001:3102: khrag gi gsum pa gzung bar bshad //
NK038(nyi)001:3103: rnal 'byor sgrub ba'i gros gyis shig /
NK038(nyi)001:3104: nga yang dam las mi g.yeng srung //
NK038(nyi)001:3105: de phyir gsang ba'i rgyud don gtad //
NK038(nyi)001:3106: ces gsungs te mi snang bar gyur to //
NK038(nyi)001:3107: 'khor 'dus pa thams cad rjes su yi rangs shing mngon par bstod do //
NK038(nyi)001:3108: dpal mgon po nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK038(nyi)001:3109: las gdams shing gtad pa'i le'u ste so drug pa'o ////
NK038(nyi)001:3110: dpal mgon nag po dur khrod mngon par rol pa mtshon cha 'khor lo'i rgyud rdzogs so //
NK038(nyi)001:3111: rgya gar gyi mkhan po bram ze gsal ba'i rgyan dang //
